NK050(wi)011:1: // bsam gtan phyi ma'i rgyud don rnam par bshad pa
NK050(wi)011:2: rig sngags 'dzin pa'i yid kyi 'dod 'jo zhes bya
NK050(wi)011:3: ba bzhugs so // na mo gu ru many+dzu g+h+ao sh+aa ya /
NK050(wi)011:4: rigs sngags yongs kyi 'khor los sgyur mchog dang //
NK050(wi)011:5: gsang 'dzin gsang ba'i bdag po rdo rje 'dzin //
NK050(wi)011:6: 'jam dpal dpal dang ldan la gus btud nas //
NK050(wi)011:7: bsam gtan phyi ma'i rgyud don rnam par bshad //
NK050(wi)011:8: de la 'dir gsang sngags dang rigs sngags rnams bsgrub
NK050(wi)011:9: pa'i thabs kyi man ngag zab mo bsam gtan phyi
NK050(wi)011:10: ma'i rim par phye ba'i rgyud 'di 'chad pa la
NK050(wi)011:17: d+h+y+aa no t+ta ra pa tra la kra ma /
NK050(wi)011:18: de nyid bod skad du bsgyur na /
NK050(wi)011:19: d+h+y+aa na bsam gtan ut+ta ra /
NK050(wi)011:20: bla ma dang phyi ma sogs la 'jug pa las skabs 'dir phyi ma /
NK050(wi)011:22: rim par phye ba zhes gsungs te /
NK050(wi)011:23: bsam gtan ni rig sngags bzla ba'i tshe sems rtse
NK050(wi)011:24: gcig pa'i bsam gtan ji ltar bya ba gang zhig
NK050(wi)011:25: / sngags 'grub pa'i thabs kyi gtso bor gyur pa de 'dir bstan na bsam gtan zhes bya zhing /
NK050(wi)011:26: de la phyi ma zhes bya ba ni /
NK050(wi)011:27: bya spyod gtsor gyur rigs sngags kyi rgyud rnam pa
NK050(wi)011:28: po gsungs pa de dag gi man ngag lta bu
NK050(wi)011:30: 'di nyid rig sngags kyi rgyud kun la dgos shing snying por gyur pa yin pa'i phyir te /
NK050(wi)011:31: rdo rje gtsug tor gyi rgyud chen po las /
NK050(wi)011:32: bzlas brjod kyi yan lag rnams kyi ming bshad kyang /
NK050(wi)011:33: de'i thabs bsam gtan ji ltar bya ba'i tshul skabs
NK050(wi)011:34: de gsal bar ma bstan pa de nyid 'dir dngos
NK050(wi)011:35: su gsal bar ston pas na de skad ces bya'o
NK050(wi)011:36: // de lta bu'i dgongs don yan lag dang bcas
NK050(wi)011:37: pa gsal bar byed pas na rim par phye ba
NK050(wi)011:38: // zhes gsungs so // gnyis pa 'gyur phyag ni /
NK050(wi)011:39: dpal rdo rje rnon po la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK050(wi)011:40: zhes bstan pa snga dar gyi dus su rgyud 'di
NK050(wi)011:41: gangs can pa'i skad du bsgyur ba'i tshe sprul pa'i
NK050(wi)011:42: lo pan chen po de dag gis 'jam dpa' rdo
NK050(wi)011:43: rje rnon po la phyag mdzad pa'o //
NK050(wi)011:45: dgos pa bstan pa dang 'brel bar gleng bslang ba rnam par dgod pa dang /
NK050(wi)011:46: bshad bya gzhung gi don rnam par bshad pa gnyis kyi /
NK050(wi)011:48: gsang sngags rgyud kyi phyogs la yang //
NK050(wi)011:50: bsam gtan gyis ni rgyas par bshad //
NK050(wi)011:51: ces pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK050(wi)011:52: bzlas brjod kyi bsam gtan dang rnal 'byor gyi mtshan nyid gang zhig /
NK050(wi)011:53: rig sngags dang gsang sngags kyi thabs kyi man ngag
NK050(wi)011:54: dam par gyur pa spang gnyen phan yon dang bcas
NK050(wi)011:56: bcom ldan 'das rdo rje 'dzin pa chen po las
NK050(wi)011:57: tshangs pa sa yi me tog ces bya bas dngos
NK050(wi)011:59: tshangs pa mi 'chi ba zhes bya ba la bstan par 'dod nas 'di skad du smras te /
NK050(wi)011:61: gasnga sngagas rgyud kyi phyogs la yang /
NK050(wi)011:62: gang zag ganga gi blo ni mchog tu mi zhena
NK050(wi)011:63: pa ste dam pa'i man ngag ldan par nan tan
NK050(wi)011:64: gyis brtags nas gting dpog pa dang mi ldan par
NK050(wi)011:66: sngags kyi don de yanga rang blo'i phyogs zhen tsam
NK050(wi)011:67: du ci dgar bzung nas don med kyi ngag smra
NK050(wi)011:68: bar spro ba ni dgos pa ci yang med pas
NK050(wi)011:69: smra ba ngan pa de dag spang bar rigs te
NK050(wi)011:70: / de dag la de lta bu /
NK050(wi)011:71: ma smras na ni mi 'tsho ba nyid du gyur
NK050(wi)011:72: pa'am ma smras thabs med pa ci zhig byung zhes
NK050(wi)011:73: pa don te / sngags kyi dgongs don rtog ge'i
NK050(wi)011:74: rigs pa sogs kyis dpyad nas chud za ba'i bshad
NK050(wi)011:75: pa 'khyams po de 'dra rang bslus gzhan bslus kyi
NK050(wi)011:76: rgyur 'gyur zhing nyes pa che ba'i phyir ro //
NK050(wi)011:77: ci'i phyir sngags rgyud kyi tshigs la dpyad nas shes par bya ba'i yul ma yin snyam na /
NK050(wi)011:78: gasnga sngagas kyi rgyud rgya mtsho chena po lta bu 'dii ni /
NK050(wi)011:79: rtog ge'i lam gyi dpe yis nye bar 'jal ba dang /
NK050(wi)011:80: mngon sum gyi tshad ma dang /
NK050(wi)011:82: de las rjesa su dapaga pa 'am /
NK050(wi)011:83: mdor na man ngag med par rang gi rnam par
NK050(wi)011:84: dpyad pa'i shesa raba kyis rtogsa para nus pa ma
NK050(wi)011:85: yina no // de'i phyir yang dag pa'i rgyud kyi lung dang /
NK050(wi)011:86: dam pa'i man ngaga gi dona dang ldan pa meda para /
NK050(wi)011:87: ganga zhig sngags kyi dgongs don du rlom pa'i lam gazhana du 'juga pa da dag /
NK050(wi)011:88: bskal pa daga ni brgya ru 'abda na yang /
NK050(wi)011:89: sngagas bzlas pa sogs kyi thabs lasa dngos grub mi thob ba //
NK050(wi)011:90: sngags kyi lunga dang de don gnad du 'byor ba'i mana ngag ma lus pa /
NK050(wi)011:91: gang zag ganga gasa yongas su spangs pa de daga la /
NK050(wi)011:92: sngags kyi grub pa nyams su myong ba la la
NK050(wi)011:93: zhig yoda dam zer na da ni mtha' gcig tu
NK050(wi)011:94: meda pa'o zhes smros par bya ba yin te /
NK050(wi)011:95: de lta bu mi srid ces pa'i tha tshig go //
NK050(wi)011:96: dasa na gasnga sngagas kyi badga nyid rgya mtsho ltar cha bar gyur pa /
NK050(wi)011:97: dangsa grub sna tshogs kyi rlabsa ni rab tu 'khrigas pa cana /
NK050(wi)011:98: phal pa'i blos bsam gyis mi khyab pa'am /
NK050(wi)011:99: bsam yas shing gting mtha' ni dapaga par daka'a ba yi /
NK050(wi)011:100: dgongs don zab mo rtogsa para nus pa gang gis
NK050(wi)011:101: de ltar sngags rgyud kyi dgongs don tshul bzhin legs
NK050(wi)011:102: par bshad na / smra ba thams cad kyi nang na smra ba' mchog tu gyur pa yin te /
NK050(wi)011:103: don che zhing zab mo rtogs par dka' ba'i gnas legs par bkral ba'i phyir ro //
NK050(wi)011:104: gal te sngags kyi gnad da ltar mi shes pa zhig na /
NK050(wi)011:105: tshangsa pa mi 'chi ba khyod kyis sngags kyi dgongs
NK050(wi)011:106: gnad zab mo ji ltar shes pa de smros shig
NK050(wi)011:107: / gal te khyod sngags kyi dgongs gnad zab mo
NK050(wi)011:108: yanga dag par smra bar ma spro na tshangs pa
NK050(wi)011:109: sa yi me tog nga yisa rdo rje 'dzin pa
NK050(wi)011:110: nyid las ji ltar thos pa'i don bashada kyis nga
NK050(wi)011:115: bdag dang sngags dang bzlas brjod kyi de nyid gsum
NK050(wi)011:116: gyi dona gal te legs par shes na dngosa grub
NK050(wi)011:118: de daga legas para mi shes na /
NK050(wi)011:119: khyod kyis sngags la brtan nas dngosa grub kyang ca zhaga 'thob ste mi 'thob bo //
NK050(wi)011:120: gzhan yang rig sngagas lasa ni rig sngagsa grub pa pa gazhana yin nam /
NK050(wi)011:121: yang na gazhana min pa gcig tu gyur pa gang yin zhes khyod la 'dri na /
NK050(wi)011:122: gal te de gnyis gang rung yin par smras na ci zhig nyes par 'gyur snyam na /
NK050(wi)011:123: gal te rig sngags dang de'i grub pa po zhes
NK050(wi)011:124: bya ba gazhana yin par gyur na 'brel ba med
NK050(wi)011:125: pas nam yang 'grub para mi 'gyur ro //
NK050(wi)011:126: 'ona te gazhana mina para bsam na /
NK050(wi)011:127: rig sngags bzung ba tsam gyis grub pa nyid du 'gyur te /
NK050(wi)011:128: de'i rgyu mtshan gal te gzhan min par 'dod pa
NK050(wi)011:129: khyod kyi ltar na khyod rig sngags 'chang ba yin
NK050(wi)011:130: pas de'i grub pa'ang de dang mnyam du tha mi
NK050(wi)011:131: dad par yod pas khyod rig sngags grub pa nyid
NK050(wi)011:132: gyur zin pasa nam mkha' la sogas para da lta
NK050(wi)011:133: nyid du thogs pa med par songa zhig /
NK050(wi)011:134: gal te rig sngags dang de'i nus pa grub pa tha mi dad cing /
NK050(wi)011:135: grub pa nyams su myong ba po'ang rig sngags de
NK050(wi)011:136: 'dzin pa po las tha dad du bya ba med
NK050(wi)011:137: pa'i phyir / grub zin par rigs pas grub kyang
NK050(wi)011:138: nam mkha' la 'gro ba sogs sngags grub pa'i yon
NK050(wi)011:139: tan dngos su snang ba da sta mi nus pa'am
NK050(wi)011:140: de lta bu ci yang yod pa mina na /
NK050(wi)011:141: sngags dang de yi grub pa gcig tu khas blangs
NK050(wi)011:142: pa 'di ni rdzun tshiga tu zad pa'am gyur pasa
NK050(wi)011:143: rigs pa mi shes pa ba langa rdza dang lhan
NK050(wi)011:144: cig ci dgar smros su rung ba tsam las /
NK050(wi)011:145: rigs pa'i lam shes pa'i mkhas pa la smra bar
NK050(wi)011:146: bya ba'i tshig nyid du mi 'gyur ro zhes smras
NK050(wi)011:147: so // de'i tshe na mi 'chi ba tshangs pa
NK050(wi)011:148: chen po pha mchod ces bya ba de nyid kyis
NK050(wi)011:149: so // / rang gi blos yongas su bsam nasa lan gyi tshig smras pa ni /
NK050(wi)011:150: gang 'dir tshangs pa sa yi me tog 'char byed ces bya ba /
NK050(wi)011:151: mi majada kyi badga posa ganga ji skad smras pa de bzhin du /
NK050(wi)011:152: rig sngags dang de'i grub pa gazhana du gyur pasa ni /
NK050(wi)011:153: rig sngags de nyid zlos pa po badga la nam
NK050(wi)011:154: yang dngos grub meda pa de ltar 'gyur mod kyi
NK050(wi)011:155: / raga sngags lasa de yi grub pa gazhana mina
NK050(wi)011:156: na rig sngags bzlas pa las byung ba'i dangsa grub
NK050(wi)011:157: de nyid rigs sngags de zlos pa po badga la
NK050(wi)011:158: grub pa nyid yod dama snyam ste /
NK050(wi)011:159: ci deltar gyur na ci zhaga nyes te nyes pa ci yang med do snyam du bdag sems la /
NK050(wi)011:160: 'on tang 'dod pa de la 'agla ba ci zhiga yod ces smras so //
NK050(wi)011:161: de la tshangs pa sa yi me tog gis lan smras pa /
NK050(wi)011:162: e ma'o tshangsa pa mi 'chi ba khyod kyi blo 'di lta bu ni /
NK050(wi)011:163: shina tu nyes pa'i dri ma meda pa daga yin par bsam nas tshig de skad smras mod kyi /
NK050(wi)011:164: shesa raba gasla ba dang ldan pa tshangs pa sa
NK050(wi)011:165: yi me tog ngasa tshul 'di la gzhig cing bsam
NK050(wi)011:166: na / tshiga re re la yang ni mi 'thad pa'i skyon gyis rnyogsa pa bazhana du mthong ste /
NK050(wi)011:167: 'di ltar khyod kyis sngags las grub pa gazhana du gyur pasa khyod la dangsa grub meda cing /
NK050(wi)011:168: gazhana mina pa'i sngags ni dngosa grub kyi rgyu yin
NK050(wi)011:169: par rigs shing 'thad pa'i phyir sngags dang grub pa
NK050(wi)011:170: gazhana min pa las sngags grub par 'adda do zhes
NK050(wi)011:171: smra ba na / tshig de 'dra smra ba ni smyon pa nyid ni yina par 'gyur te /
NK050(wi)011:172: gong du bshad pa ltar sngags dang de'i grub pa
NK050(wi)011:173: gzhan min pas na sngags gzung ba tsam gyis grub
NK050(wi)011:174: par gyur te me bzung bas bsreg pa dngos su
NK050(wi)011:175: snang ba dang tshul mtshungs par 'gyur ro //
NK050(wi)011:176: sngags bzung yang grub pa mi snang na de gcig
NK050(wi)011:177: yin par yang ji ltar smra rigs te sngags yod
NK050(wi)011:178: kyang grub pa med pas tha mi dad kyi gcig
NK050(wi)011:179: la gcig yod pa dang gcig med pa'i khyad par
NK050(wi)011:180: ji ltar rung / des na gcig tu'ang grub pa
NK050(wi)011:181: med par 'gyur te sngags dang de grub pa tha
NK050(wi)011:182: dad du 'gyur ro zhes smras so //
NK050(wi)011:183: de nas tshangs pa mi 'chi bas smras pa /
NK050(wi)011:184: 'agro ba'i bdag po zhes tshangs pa chen po sa
NK050(wi)011:185: yi me tog nyid la bos nas ja ltar na
NK050(wi)011:186: gsang sngags dang rigs sngags rnams las dngosa grub mi
NK050(wi)011:187: bslu bar yada para khasa 'acha ba /
NK050(wi)011:188: ye shesa kyi sgron mara gyur pa khyod kyis /
NK050(wi)011:189: bdag la ja ltar phana pa bashada du gasla zhes zhus so //
NK050(wi)011:190: de la tshangs pa chen po sa yi me tog gis smras pa /
NK050(wi)011:191: badga gasa rnam para dpyad na ni /
NK050(wi)011:192: riga sngags lasa de'i grub pa nyid gzhan nama mi gzhan pa yang min cing /
NK050(wi)011:193: de ltar gazhana min dang mi gazhana pa yang ma yina pasa na /
NK050(wi)011:194: rgyu mtshan de nyid kyi phyir /
NK050(wi)011:195: sngags las dngos grub thob pa yod la /
NK050(wi)011:196: badga ni sngags de nyid sgrub pa po rang gis
NK050(wi)011:197: yid la zhen par bsams te yang yang gamas pa
NK050(wi)011:198: lasa nam zhig nus pa mthu can du gyur nas
NK050(wi)011:200: rgyu rkyen rten 'brel gyi dbang gis snang ba'i chos
NK050(wi)011:201: nyid mtha' gzhan du brtag par dka' yang bslu ba
NK050(wi)011:202: med par snang zhing don byed pa nyid du 'dod
NK050(wi)011:203: do // de ltar goms pa las dngos grub 'byar ba'i 'thad pa brjod pa /
NK050(wi)011:204: shasa bya thams cad kyi nang na bla na med
NK050(wi)011:205: pa ganga yin pa'i rnam pa thams cad mkhyen pa'i
NK050(wi)011:206: ye shes de yang rang gis lam goms pa las
NK050(wi)011:207: 'thob par 'gyur na gsang sngags las kyi cho ga
NK050(wi)011:208: khyad par can 'di dag gis gnas skabs dang mthar
NK050(wi)011:209: thug gi dngos grub 'thob tu yada pa ca zhiga
NK050(wi)011:210: smos te smos mi dgos so //
NK050(wi)011:211: de yang bzlas brjod kyi de kho na nyid dang /
NK050(wi)011:212: lha yi de kho na nyid dang /
NK050(wi)011:213: badga ga de kho na nyid /
NK050(wi)011:214: sangs rgyas kyis rgyud rnams su gsungs pa 'di ja lta ba ni /
NK050(wi)011:215: gansa rten te 'jig rten pa'i lha chen po sogs
NK050(wi)011:216: kyis bshad pa'i rgyud dang rig byed sogs gzhung gazhana
NK050(wi)011:217: la med para gyur pa de yis ni /
NK050(wi)011:218: sangs rgyas kyis gsungs pa'i sngags kyi cho ga 'di
NK050(wi)011:219: lta bu 'jig rten gsum na mtshungsa pa meda par
NK050(wi)011:220: / tshangs pa sa yi me tog badga gis rtogs so //
NK050(wi)011:221: skabs 'dir bish+ta bam zhes pa gnas rten te /
NK050(wi)011:222: 'gro ba dang srid pa gnas rten rnams 'jig rten
NK050(wi)011:223: gyi ming gi rnam grangs su bshad pa'i gnas rten
NK050(wi)011:225: de ltar gleng bslang pa'i tshiga snga ma lasa phyi ma'i tshiga tu 'phrosa pa byas pa las /
NK050(wi)011:226: tshangs pa chen po mi 'chi ba zhes bya ba
NK050(wi)011:227: sngags kyi dngos grub 'doda pa skal pa chena po
NK050(wi)011:228: pa des / bya rgyud rdo rje gtsug tor gyi
NK050(wi)011:229: rgyud kyi phyogs gcig bzlas brjod kyi man ngag bsam
NK050(wi)011:230: gtan phyi ma 'di ni nyan para byed par gyur
NK050(wi)011:231: pa des / to // da nasa tshangsa pa chen
NK050(wi)011:232: pa mi 'chi pha mchod da nyid kyis rdo rje
NK050(wi)011:233: gtsug tor gyi rgyud sngar nyan pa la /
NK050(wi)011:234: tshangs pa chen po sa ya ma tog 'achara phyed pasa /
NK050(wi)011:235: rdo rje gtsug tor gyi rgyud kyi man ngag /
NK050(wi)011:236: sngags bzla tshul gyi bsam gtan gyisa ni brgyan para byas pa 'di nyid bshad do //
NK050(wi)011:237: zhes 'di yan chad tshig kha gsal bas 'grel pa
NK050(wi)011:238: mi dgos par dgongs nas sangs rgyas gsang ba'i 'grel
NK050(wi)011:239: bar ma bshad la 'grel ba gzhan yang ma mthong
NK050(wi)011:240: mod / tshig gi 'bru gnon cung zad 'dir bgyis
NK050(wi)011:241: pa yin la ha cang nor dogs chen po mi
NK050(wi)011:242: snang yang cung zad res tshig sbyar tshul la skyed
NK050(wi)011:243: 'don rgyu 'dra mthong na mkhas pa dag gis de
NK050(wi)011:245: gnyis pa bshad bya gzhung gi don la /
NK050(wi)011:246: dgos pa bstan cing yid ches pa'i lo rgyus bcas bshad par dam bcas pa dang /
NK050(wi)011:247: bshad bya dngos bshad pa gnyis /
NK050(wi)011:249: de nas ye shes kun rdzogs pa //
NK050(wi)011:251: rtag tu rgyun du sbyor bar bya //
NK050(wi)011:252: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK050(wi)011:253: de ltar gleng bslang ba'i rjes thog /
NK050(wi)011:254: de nasa 'phags pa'i ye shesa chen po kun nas
NK050(wi)011:255: rdzogsa pa nyid du byed pa ni rig sngags yin
NK050(wi)011:256: la / riga sngagas dang gasang sngagas de nyid sgrub
NK050(wi)011:257: pa'i thabas chen po nyid du gyur pa ganga de
NK050(wi)011:258: la / ni / 'di ltar bsam gtan ldan pa'i
NK050(wi)011:259: yid kyi las phra ba 'di nyid ston pa mtshungs
NK050(wi)011:260: pa med pa da bzhiina gshegas pasa gsungs shing /
NK050(wi)011:261: lha chen po sogs kyis bshad pa'i bzlas brjod kyi tshul rnams las 'phags pa'i gdams pa gang zhig /
NK050(wi)011:262: bdag gi de kho na nyid la dmigs pa sogs
NK050(wi)011:263: bsam gtan khyad par can gyisa kyang shin tu brgyan
NK050(wi)011:264: pa dang / srog rtsol bsdam pa sogs lha'i rnala
NK050(wi)011:265: 'byor du byed pa'i thabas na kun tu rdzogs par
NK050(wi)011:266: pa dang / bstan pa / de nyid kyi sgo nas lus sems kyi sdug bsngal dang /
NK050(wi)011:267: de'i rgyu sdiga pa ma lus pa sela ba ste /
NK050(wi)011:268: de lta bu'i thabs 'di nyid gsang 'dzin dpa' bo
NK050(wi)011:269: phyag na rda rje'i zhala nasa tshangs pa sa yi
NK050(wi)011:270: me tog bdag la dngos su gsungsa pa'o //
NK050(wi)011:271: tshul 'di dang ldan par byas pa'i yon tan gyi
NK050(wi)011:272: khyad par ni 'khor ba'i skye ba dang 'chi ba
NK050(wi)011:274: sems can thams cad kyi gnod sbyor gyis yul dus kun tu ma tshugsa shing /
NK050(wi)011:275: rang gi sems dbang du gyur nas bartan par byed pa ste /
NK050(wi)011:276: de ltar 'jig rten 'ad dang pha rola tu yon
NK050(wi)011:277: tan gyi 'bras bus de lta bu dag byed para
NK050(wi)011:279: thabs gong bshad de las rigs gsum gyi dkyil 'khora chen pa rnams dang /
NK050(wi)011:280: la sogas pa'i sgras de yi rigs su gtogs pa rnams 'byunga zhing /
NK050(wi)011:282: mdor na mngon par mtho ba dang nges par legs
NK050(wi)011:283: pa gang 'adda pa'i dana ni rje sa su sgrub
NK050(wi)011:284: par nus so // de ltar thabs kyi yon tan
NK050(wi)011:285: bstan nas de nyid bshad par dam bca' ba ni
NK050(wi)011:286: par nus so // / cho ga'am bya ba ganga
NK050(wi)011:287: dang ganga daga gis bzlas brjod dang ming gnas sogs
NK050(wi)011:288: bsam gatan gyi lasa sam bya ba la /
NK050(wi)011:289: ganga ji ltar gansa pa yi tshul de ni /
NK050(wi)011:290: da bazhana gshegs pa la phyag 'tshal nasa /
NK050(wi)011:291: da daga ma lus bdag gis bashada para bya'o //
NK050(wi)011:294: rig sngags de nyid ma lus dang /
NK050(wi)011:295: zhes sogs tshigs su bcad pa'i don bzhin /
NK050(wi)011:296: de nyid gsum legs par shes shing /
NK050(wi)011:297: de'i don la rtse gcig mnyam par bzhag pa'i bsam
NK050(wi)011:298: gtan dang ldan par gyur na dngos grub tshegs med
NK050(wi)011:299: par thob par nges pa'i phyir /
NK050(wi)011:300: thog mar de lta bu'i bsam gtan gyi basngagasa pa brjod pa /
NK050(wi)011:301: gsang sngags bsam gtan zhes bya ba la sogs pas bstan te /
NK050(wi)011:302: gasang sngagas de yi bsam gtan zhasa bya ba /
NK050(wi)011:303: snod min la mchog tu gasnga ba rgyud so so
NK050(wi)011:304: na yang snying po lta bur gyur pa'i man ngag
NK050(wi)011:305: 'di 'dra gsal por ma bstan cing sbas par gyur
NK050(wi)011:306: pa 'di ni rgyal ba nyid kyis rdo rje gtsug
NK050(wi)011:307: tor gyi rgyud kyi phyogs gcig bsam gtan phyi ma
NK050(wi)011:308: 'dir ma sbas par yang dag par gsungsa pa yin
NK050(wi)011:309: la / sgo gsum nyes pa med par drang por srong ba'i drang srong gang zhig /
NK050(wi)011:310: khrus dang gtsang sbra sbyang ba sogs kyi daka'a thub chen po can de dag gi yanga /
NK050(wi)011:311: sngags bzlas pa'i bsam gtan gyi thabs da daga meda
NK050(wi)011:312: na sngags bzlas pa la cher brtson kyang ma 'grub
NK050(wi)011:313: pa yin na phal pa ma bsdam pa dag gis
NK050(wi)011:314: lta ci smros te mi 'grub bo //
NK050(wi)011:315: gsang sngags tshul bzhin sgrub pa'i thabs dang ldan pa
NK050(wi)011:316: bdag nyid lhar bsgom pa'i rnal 'byor cana de rnams
NK050(wi)011:317: kyis / gasnga sngags kyi bzlas barjada gang zhig /
NK050(wi)011:318: dper na me 'abra ba dang 'dra ba sgrib gnyis kyi bud shing sreg par byed cing /
NK050(wi)011:319: byin rlabs kyi tsha dbal che zhing rno ba nyid
NK050(wi)011:320: du gyur pas skye ba da nga 'chi ba sogs
NK050(wi)011:321: kyi sdug bsngal 'ajaga par byed pa 'di lta bu
NK050(wi)011:322: ni rdo rja can gyis sngon bdag la gsungsa sa
NK050(wi)011:324: da 'dra gsang sngags kyi bsam gtan gang zhig gsal bar snang zhing /
NK050(wi)011:325: des yid la re ba'i 'bras su stsol bas rang sems yongs su tshim par bya ba'am /
NK050(wi)011:326: yang na bsam gtan gyi bde bas rang rgyud yongs
NK050(wi)011:327: su tshim par bya ba bsam gtan me lta bu
NK050(wi)011:328: de daga la / sngags kyi dangos grub 'adda pa dag gisa ni /
NK050(wi)011:329: nyi ma re re bzhin rtaga para rgyun tu sbyor bar bya ste /
NK050(wi)011:330: 'dod pa'i 'bras bu mngon du gyur gyi bar brtson pa mi gtong bar bya'o //
NK050(wi)011:331: de ltar bzlas brjod kyi bsam gtan la basngagasa pa sngon du btang nas /
NK050(wi)011:332: bsam gtan dngos bshad pa la /
NK050(wi)011:333: de nyid gsum spyir bstan pa dang /
NK050(wi)011:334: bzlas brjod kyi de nyid bye brag tu bshad pa gnyis kyi dang po la /
NK050(wi)011:338: lha yi sku yi gnas de la //
NK050(wi)011:340: bzlas brjod gzhan du mi bya'o //
NK050(wi)011:341: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK050(wi)011:342: 'di dag gi spyi don mdor bsdus sngon du brjod na go bde bas de bshad pa la /
NK050(wi)011:344: rnal 'byor thabs ni kun bstan pa //
NK050(wi)011:345: zhes gsungs pa bzhin du mchog dang thun mong gi
NK050(wi)011:346: dngos grub bde zhing myur bar bsgrub pa'i thabs ni
NK050(wi)011:348: gtso bo bzlas brjod kyi yan lag dang /
NK050(wi)011:349: de'i grogs su nges par dgos pa dbang nod pa dang dam tshig bzung ba sngon du song nas /
NK050(wi)011:350: gtsang sbra dang sbyin sreg mchod pa sogs las kyi
NK050(wi)011:351: bya ba sna tshogs ma nyams par nyams su len
NK050(wi)011:352: pa yin no // lam dngos ni de nyid gsum gyis bsdus te /
NK050(wi)011:353: dang po bsgrub bya rig sngags kyi de kho na nyid ni /
NK050(wi)011:354: 'bras bu mthar phyin pa'i ye shes kyi sku de bzhin gshegs pa'am /
NK050(wi)011:355: de'i sras kyi thu bo'i tshul du ston pa /
NK050(wi)011:358: phyag na rdo rje 'dzin pa lta bu chos kyi
NK050(wi)011:359: dbyings dang gnyis su med pa'i ye shes chen po
NK050(wi)011:360: nyid rnam par rtags kyi phyag rgyar shar ba'i sku
NK050(wi)011:361: yi dbyibs dang / rig sngags kyi sgra dang /
NK050(wi)011:362: phyag rgya ut+pala la sogs pa'i rnam par snang ba la brjod do //
NK050(wi)011:363: bsam bya lha yi rang bzhin de la dbye na /
NK050(wi)011:366: don dam pa'i lha dang gsum /
NK050(wi)011:367: dang po la'ang spyan sogs yan lag rnams kyi cha dang ldan pa'i yan lag can gyi sku dang /
NK050(wi)011:368: de'i phyag rgya 'khor lo dang rdo rje la sogs pa gnyis su yod cing /
NK050(wi)011:369: sgra yi lha la sgra gdangs dang /
NK050(wi)011:370: yi ge'i gzugs kyis rnam par phye ba gnyis /
NK050(wi)011:371: dang po sgrar brjod pa'i yi ge la'ang /
NK050(wi)011:372: sgra gdangs tsam la dmigs pa'i yid bzlas dang /
NK050(wi)011:374: yig 'bru re re la sems pa'i rtogs pa dang gsum mo //
NK050(wi)011:376: chos kyi dbyings dang de la dmigs pa rnam par mi rtog pa'i ye shes dang gnyis so //
NK050(wi)011:377: sgrub pa po bdag gi de kho na nyid ni /
NK050(wi)011:378: 'di ltar 'khor bar bde sdug myong ba pa dang /
NK050(wi)011:379: rnam par grol ba 'thob pa'i rten du gyur ba
NK050(wi)011:380: ni phung po lnga'i bdag nyid can 'di las gzhan
NK050(wi)011:381: du med la / phung po lnga po ni du
NK050(wi)011:382: ma tshogs pa dang skad cig mar 'byung ba'i rgyun
NK050(wi)011:383: du med la / tsam yin gyi / 'di la
NK050(wi)011:384: bdag ces bya ba ngo bos sgrub pa gang yang
NK050(wi)011:385: du med la / tsam yin gyi / med mod
NK050(wi)011:386: / rten cing 'brel bar 'byung ba'i snang ba la
NK050(wi)011:387: skur ba gdab tu mi rung ba sgyu ma lta
NK050(wi)011:388: bu 'di tsam la bdag gi de kho na nyid
NK050(wi)011:390: yang dag par dpyad na tshogs pa dang rgyun rdzas su med la /
NK050(wi)011:391: chos so so ba tshogs pa la yan lag can
NK050(wi)011:392: zhes pa btags pa tsam las rdzas su ma grub
NK050(wi)011:393: cing / yan lag rnams kyang rdul phra rab dang
NK050(wi)011:394: skad cig ma'i char yang grub pa med pas gzhi
NK050(wi)011:395: rtsa dang bral bzhin rten 'byung gi snang ba chu
NK050(wi)011:396: zla lta bu 'gog pa med pa yin pas /
NK050(wi)011:397: bdag de ni gzugs sogs kyi rnam pa gang du'ang mi 'byed de shes par byar med la /
NK050(wi)011:398: bdag des gzugs sogs la dmigs shing 'byed pa'ang rnam par spangs pas /
NK050(wi)011:400: de dag phan tshun tu ldan pa min /
NK050(wi)011:401: bdag gis phung po la dbang bsgyur ba'ang min pas /
NK050(wi)011:402: bdag tu 'dogs pa'i kun rtog thams cad kyi spyod
NK050(wi)011:403: yul las grol ba yan lag med pa'am yan lag
NK050(wi)011:404: rnam par grol ba zhes bya'o //
NK050(wi)011:405: gal te rnam par shes pas yul thams cad la
NK050(wi)011:406: longs spyod cing de dang de'i tha snyad byed pas
NK050(wi)011:407: na bdag rnam shes tsam yin no snyam na /
NK050(wi)011:408: kun tu rtog pa'i bag chags kyi dbang gis rmi lam ltar gzung 'dzin du snang ba'i dus na /
NK050(wi)011:409: longs spyod bya dang spyod byed du snang mod kyi /
NK050(wi)011:410: sems de'i rang gi ngo bor grub pa rdul phra
NK050(wi)011:411: rab kyi cha tsam yang phyi na'ang med nang na'ang
NK050(wi)011:412: med / dbyibs dang kha dog sogs chos gang gi
NK050(wi)011:413: rnam par yang grub pa med pas sems de ni
NK050(wi)011:414: de bzhin gshegs pa'i spyan lngas kyang blta bar byar
NK050(wi)011:415: med pa phra ba rtogs dka' ba rang bzhin gyis
NK050(wi)011:416: stong pa yin pas mdor na bdag dang phung po
NK050(wi)011:417: dang rnam rig gi spros pa kun las 'das pa
NK050(wi)011:418: med / yin no // 'grel pa las bdag gi
NK050(wi)011:419: de kho na nyid ni rigs pas dpyad pa'i stong
NK050(wi)011:421: bdag gi de kha na nyid gnyis su med pa'i
NK050(wi)011:422: ye shes kyi mtshan nyid de thob na sangs rgyas
NK050(wi)011:424: mdor na rnam par shes pa'i mtshan nyid kyi chos
NK050(wi)011:425: las 'das te snang stong gnyis su med pa'i ye
NK050(wi)011:426: shes kyi bzhugs tshul gtan la phabs na /
NK050(wi)011:427: bdag gi de kho na nyid kyang de yin la
NK050(wi)011:428: don dam pa'i lha yang de tshul gcig ste chos
NK050(wi)011:429: thams cad kyi gnas lugs dang don dam byang chub
NK050(wi)011:431: tshul de la mnyam par bzhag na mtshan med kyi rnal 'byor kyang yin no //
NK050(wi)011:432: de'i phyir slob dpon gyi 'grel par bdag gi de kho na nyid ni /
NK050(wi)011:433: bdag dang phung po rnam rig gi spros pa las
NK050(wi)011:434: 'das pa'am yan lag med pa zhes spyir bstan nas
NK050(wi)011:436: dmigs pa gzugs sogs med pa /
NK050(wi)011:437: dmigs byed kyi rnam pa med pa /
NK050(wi)011:440: rang rig pas gsal bar rjes su myong ba ste mtshan nyid lnga'am drug ldan du gsungs so //
NK050(wi)011:441: de lta bu'i bdag gi de kho na nyid gtan
NK050(wi)011:442: la phabs nas de la blo bzhag par bya zhing
NK050(wi)011:443: / de'i rjes su lha'i rang bzhin du bsgom pa ni kri ya lha drug ces grags pa ste /
NK050(wi)011:444: dang po stong pa'i lha ni /
NK050(wi)011:445: bdag dang lha'i de nyid rnam par mi rtog pa'i
NK050(wi)011:446: dbyings su ro gcig cing khyad med pas bdag dang
NK050(wi)011:447: lha rang bzhin gcig pa'i nges shes sam nga rgyal
NK050(wi)011:448: du bya'o zhes gsungs te snang ba med pa'i ting
NK050(wi)011:449: nge 'dzin no // de'i ngang las lha gang yin
NK050(wi)011:450: gyi sngags kyi yi ge'i sgra gdangs tsam nam mkha'
NK050(wi)011:451: las grags par bsam pa sgra'i lha'o //
NK050(wi)011:452: gdangs de las sngags kyi yi ge'i gzugs kyi rnam
NK050(wi)011:453: par nam mkha' la snang ba ni yi ge'i lha'o
NK050(wi)011:454: // de nas gzugs kyi lha mngon du rdzogs par bya ba'i phyir /
NK050(wi)011:455: bdag gi de kho na nyid zla ba'i dkyil 'khor
NK050(wi)011:456: gyi rnam par gyur pa'i steng du lha'i ngo bo
NK050(wi)011:457: sngags kyi yi ge de dag 'dus te /
NK050(wi)011:458: dag pa'i dngul chu gser gyi phye ma la zhen
NK050(wi)011:459: pa ltar 'dres pa las bdag dang lha gnyis su
NK050(wi)011:460: med pa gcig tu gyur pa'i rang bzhin las 'od
NK050(wi)011:461: 'phros 'phags pa mchod sems can gyi don byas pa
NK050(wi)011:462: sogs kyi sa sgo nas lhag pa'i lha'i gzugs gang
NK050(wi)011:463: yin pa gsal zhing de ltar yin pa'i nga rgyal
NK050(wi)011:464: bya ba ni gzugs kyi lha'o //
NK050(wi)011:465: de nas de'i mtshog ma dang spyi gtsug sogs su
NK050(wi)011:466: lha gang yin pa'i rigs kyi phyag rgyas btab pas
NK050(wi)011:467: brtan zhing byin gyis rlobs pa ni phyag rgya'i lha'o
NK050(wi)011:468: // de nas de lta bu'i lha de'i sku dang
NK050(wi)011:469: yan lag gi cha shas re re nas kyang gsal
NK050(wi)011:470: btab la de'i mtshan ma la sems bzung zhing 'di
NK050(wi)011:471: dang 'di lta bu zhes brtag pa la rgyun du
NK050(wi)011:473: rtog pa'i lha'am kun rdzob kyi sku'am mtshan ma'i lha zhes bya'o //
NK050(wi)011:474: de lta bu'i mtshan bcas lha'i rnal 'byor gyi bsam
NK050(wi)011:475: gtan de nyid sroog rtsol bsdam pa'i sbyor bas gcun
NK050(wi)011:476: nas bsgom pas / mthar rtsol ba med par rtog
NK050(wi)011:477: pa dang bral te mngon du gsal ba na ting
NK050(wi)011:478: nge 'dzin la gnas pa yin no //
NK050(wi)011:479: de ltar lha sku'i rnal 'byor dang ldan pa'i sgo nas bzlas brjod byed pa la /
NK050(wi)011:480: bzlas brjod kyi de kho na nyid ni yan lag bzhi dang ldan pa ste /
NK050(wi)011:481: gzhung gi dkyus su 'chad par 'gyur ro //
NK050(wi)011:482: da ni gzhung gi tshig don bshad par bya ste /
NK050(wi)011:483: 'di ltar rig sngags kyi bzlas brjod byed par 'dod pas /
NK050(wi)011:484: rang gis gang bsgrub par bya ba'i lha yi sku
NK050(wi)011:485: dngos su dmigs pa'am sku de ya gansa sam rten
NK050(wi)011:486: ri mor bris pa la sogs pa de la /
NK050(wi)011:487: sngags bzla ba'i dang po kha nara me tog la
NK050(wi)011:488: sogs pa'i mchoda pa byas nas ni zhes des mtshon
NK050(wi)011:489: nas gtsang sbra la gnas shing bdag gnas yo byad
NK050(wi)011:491: tshogs zhing spyan drangs pa sdig pa bshags pa lus
NK050(wi)011:492: dbul ba sogs cho ga'i sbyor ba rnams shugs kyis
NK050(wi)011:493: bstan pa nyid du shes par bya'o //
NK050(wi)011:494: de nas bzlas pa'i rnal 'byor gyi phyir /
NK050(wi)011:495: bde ba'i stan la skyil krung la sogs pa'i gnas bcas te 'dug cing /
NK050(wi)011:497: yang na dmigs pa la rtse gcig tu byed pa'i
NK050(wi)011:498: rnal 'byor gyi gansa bacasa pa'am bzung zhing zhes so
NK050(wi)011:499: // sgrub byed kyi thabs shes pa'i shes raba cana sgrub pa po des /
NK050(wi)011:500: bde bar bashagas pa nyid rang gi mdun du bsam nasa ni /
NK050(wi)011:501: bzlas pa sogs las kyi sbyor ba thams cad bcom ldan 'das kyi spyan sngar bya'o //
NK050(wi)011:502: de'i rjes su'am phyi nasa bdag gi de kho na
NK050(wi)011:503: nyid mig sogs yan lag gi chos su gdags pa
NK050(wi)011:504: kun las rnam par grol ba' phyir na de nyid
NK050(wi)011:505: yul gzugs su mi 'byed pa'am mi dmigs shing /
NK050(wi)011:506: yul can blos gzugs sogs chos su 'dzin pa'am 'byed
NK050(wi)011:507: pa'i rnama pa spangsa te gzung 'dzin med pa 'jig
NK050(wi)011:508: rten pa'i shes pa yul min pa phra la rtogs
NK050(wi)011:509: dka' ba ste rnam par shes pa'i ngo bo tsam
NK050(wi)011:511: spros pa dang bral bar rang bzhin 'od gsal ba
NK050(wi)011:512: don dam byang chub sems kyi rang bzhin so so
NK050(wi)011:513: rang rig pa'i shes rab kyis rtogs nas de'i ngang
NK050(wi)011:515: rgod pa sogs kyis mi g.yo bar gnas kyang /
NK050(wi)011:516: rmug pa sogs dang bral bas gasla ba ste mtshan nyid drug ldan de lta bu'i don de ni /
NK050(wi)011:517: sgrub pa po'i blo yi dpyod pa ste so so
NK050(wi)011:518: rang rig pa'i shes rab kyi madun na gansa pa
NK050(wi)011:520: badga gi de kho na nyid 'di 'drara blo bazhaga nasa na /
NK050(wi)011:521: de'i rjes su lha'i de kho na nyid dam sngagas
NK050(wi)011:522: kyi de kho na nyid kyi rnam par shesa pasa
NK050(wi)011:523: bsgoma par bya ba ni gong lha drug tu bstan
NK050(wi)011:524: pa bzhin no // de ltar lhar snang la sems
NK050(wi)011:525: bsdama nasa bzhag pas mthar rtsol ba med par rtog
NK050(wi)011:526: med du gsal ba'i ting nga 'dzina la gansa par
NK050(wi)011:528: sems bsdam pa'i tshul bzlas brjod kyi yan lag dang bcas pa rgyas par gsungs pa /
NK050(wi)011:529: srog rlung dang rtsol ba dran pa ste de gnyis
NK050(wi)011:530: raba tu bsdama pa ni srog rtsol bsdam pa zhes
NK050(wi)011:532: de dang ldan pa'i sgo nas bzlas brjod bya'o zhes so //
NK050(wi)011:533: rgyud gzhan rnam snang mngon byang las kyang /
NK050(wi)011:534: srog ces bya ba rlung du bshad /
NK050(wi)011:535: rtsol pa dran pa zhes bya'o //
NK050(wi)011:536: de gnyis bsdam par byas nas su /
NK050(wi)011:538: zhes gsungs pa ltar srog ni rnam rtog g.yo ba'i bzhon pa rlung yin te /
NK050(wi)011:539: 'di ltar mig dang rna ba sogs dbang po'i sgo dang /
NK050(wi)011:540: mtshan ma dang bu ga skra dang ba spu'i mthar
NK050(wi)011:541: thug par rgyu ba rnams rus sbal gyi lus bskum
NK050(wi)011:542: zhing lce yis / chu 'jib pa'i tshul ltar nang
NK050(wi)011:543: du bsdus te rlung 'byin 'jug de dag rang sar
NK050(wi)011:544: zhing lce yis / dgag pa dang / rtsol ba
NK050(wi)011:545: ni skabs 'dir dran pa ste sems kyi 'bad rtsol
NK050(wi)011:546: sna tshogs g.yo ba de nyid bkag nas gang la
NK050(wi)011:547: dmigs pa de nyid las gzhan du mi g.yo bar
NK050(wi)011:549: de lta bu'i phyir srog rtsol bsdam pa zhes bya'o //
NK050(wi)011:550: skabs gzhan du srog ste rlung gi g.yo ba rtsol bas bkag pa dang /
NK050(wi)011:551: rlung rang gnas su bcing pas 'chi ba med pa'i
NK050(wi)011:552: srog rtsol sdom par byed pa la srog rtsol du
NK050(wi)011:554: skabs 'dir gong ltar shes par bya'o //
NK050(wi)011:555: tshul de dang ldan pa'i sgo nas bzlas brjod kyi de kho na nyid bshad pa /
NK050(wi)011:556: sngags kyi yi ge'i phreng ba'i sgra dang /
NK050(wi)011:557: byang chub semas kyi ngo bo zla ba'i dkyil 'khor rnam par dag pa dang /
NK050(wi)011:558: gzhi dang po mdun gyi de bzhin gshegs pa'i sku
NK050(wi)011:559: la dmigs pa gzhoola ba dang de brtan par gyur
NK050(wi)011:560: pa na gasnga sngags ma 'gyur ba'i gazha zhes bya
NK050(wi)011:561: ste / gzhi gzhan la'ang brtan par gyur nas gsang
NK050(wi)011:562: sngags mi 'gyur ba'i gzhi zhes sbyar te shes par
NK050(wi)011:563: ste / bya'o // yang na gsang sngags mi 'gyur
NK050(wi)011:564: ba'i gzhi zhes mar sbyar na'ang rung ste gzhi phyi
NK050(wi)011:565: ma 'di rang nyid lha'i rnam par bsgom pa yin
NK050(wi)011:566: ste / bya'o // la / bdag gi de kho na nyid kyang de yin no //
NK050(wi)011:567: gsang sngags mi 'gyur zhes bar gyi gsal byed kyi
NK050(wi)011:568: tshig de don la yan lag bzhi po dus gcig
NK050(wi)011:569: gsal zhing brtan par gyur pa la gsang sngags mi
NK050(wi)011:571: de ltar sngags kyi sgra dang /
NK050(wi)011:572: byang chub sems zla dkyil dang /
NK050(wi)011:573: bdag mdun lha'i rnam par bsgom pa'i gzhi gnyis te
NK050(wi)011:574: yan lag bzhi po de dang ldan na yan lag
NK050(wi)011:575: ma nyamsa pa'i bzlas brjod kyi de kho na nyid
NK050(wi)011:576: yin pas / de lta bu'i tshul du gsang sngags
NK050(wi)011:577: nyid yid bzlas sam shub bur ci nus su bzlas
NK050(wi)011:579: de yang rnam snang mngon byang las /
NK050(wi)011:580: yi ge dang ni yi ge sbyar //
NK050(wi)011:581: de bzhin gzhi las gzhir gyur pa //
NK050(wi)011:582: shin tu bsdam pa'i yid la ni //
NK050(wi)011:584: yi ge byang chub sems yin te //
NK050(wi)011:585: gnyis pa sgra zhes bya ba yin //
NK050(wi)011:586: gzhi ni rang gi lha gzhag pa //
NK050(wi)011:587: rang gi lus kyi gnas la bya //
NK050(wi)011:588: gzhi gnyis pa ni rdzogs sangs rgyas //
NK050(wi)011:589: rkang gnyis mchog tu shes par bya //
NK050(wi)011:590: zla ba'i dkyil 'khor rnams dag pa //
NK050(wi)011:591: sngags pas de la gnas par bsam //
NK050(wi)011:592: yi ge rnams ni go rim bzhin //
NK050(wi)011:593: de yi dbus su legs par dgod //
NK050(wi)011:594: slar sdud pa yi tshig gis non //
NK050(wi)011:595: srog dang rtsol ba rnam par sbyangs //
NK050(wi)011:596: zhes gsungs pa ltar rgyud dag las sngar /
NK050(wi)011:597: ngag gi bzlas brjod med par bsam gtan gyi sgo nas sngags 'grub pa dang /
NK050(wi)011:598: rnal 'byor thar ba thob par gsungs na yang /
NK050(wi)011:599: yan lag gang la dmigs nas bzlas brjod bya ba dang /
NK050(wi)011:600: yid bzlas dang shub bzlas byed tshul sogs gsal por
NK050(wi)011:601: ma bstan pa rgyud 'dir gsal bar bstan pa'i bsam
NK050(wi)011:602: gtan gyi phyi ma zhes mtshan du thogs pa'ang yin
NK050(wi)011:603: no // de yang rang lha'i rnal 'byor du gsal
NK050(wi)011:604: ba'i zlos pa pos rang gi mdun du bzhugs pa'i
NK050(wi)011:605: de bzhin gshegs pa'i thugs kar byang chub sems kyi
NK050(wi)011:606: rang bzhin zla ba'i dkyil 'khor rnam par dag pa
NK050(wi)011:607: la bkod pa'i gsang sngags kyi yi ge'i phreng ba
NK050(wi)011:608: la dmigs nas srog rtsol bsdams te bzla bar bya
NK050(wi)011:609: no // ba yin no // de ltar sgra dang
NK050(wi)011:610: sems dang bdag dang lha'i gzhi bzhi po 'di ni
NK050(wi)011:611: dngos grub 'byung ba'i gzhi yin pas gzhi bzhi zhes
NK050(wi)011:612: no // ba yin no // bya la / bdag
NK050(wi)011:613: gi gzhi zhes brjod pa ni sems dang sems byung
NK050(wi)011:614: sogs phung po'i chos 'di dag sems can phal pa
NK050(wi)011:615: rnams kyis bdag dang gzhan tu rtog pa'i gzhi yin
NK050(wi)011:616: no // ba yin no // bya la / la
NK050(wi)011:617: / 'dir bdag gzhan lha'i ngo bos dngos grub 'byung
NK050(wi)011:618: ba'i gzhi nyid du gyur pa la bya'o //
NK050(wi)011:619: 'di bzhi dang ldan pa'i ting nge 'dzin dang ma bral na sngags kyi yan lag ma nyams la /
NK050(wi)011:620: bral na nyams pa yin no //
NK050(wi)011:621: yan lag snga ma gsum mdun gyi lha'i gzhir bsgom pa'i dmigs pa ma btang ba dang /
NK050(wi)011:622: bdag gi gzhi la nga rgyal ma btang bar gzhi
NK050(wi)011:623: bzhi dus gcig gsal ba'i ngang du gnas par bya
NK050(wi)011:624: zhes gsungs / gal te ngala bar gyur na bdag
NK050(wi)011:625: dang mdun gyi lha dang sngags kyi dmigs pa btang
NK050(wi)011:626: zhes gsungs / ste / bdag gi lus tha mal
NK050(wi)011:627: bar bsam pas ldang la ngala sosa par gyis shiga
NK050(wi)011:628: zhes gsungs / ste / / ces gsungs te /
NK050(wi)011:630: mdun gyi yi ge'i yig 'bru'i dbyibs la sems pas /
NK050(wi)011:631: sgra gdangs la dmigs pa btang ngo //
NK050(wi)011:632: yi ge'i dmigs pa btang ste zla dkyil tsam dang /
NK050(wi)011:633: de btang ste de bzhin gshegs pa'i sku tsam dang /
NK050(wi)011:634: de btang ste rang lha'i skur gsal ba de'i thugs
NK050(wi)011:635: ka'i sgra dang yig 'bru dang zla ba dang lha
NK050(wi)011:636: sku dang / rnam par mi rtog pa'i ngo bo ye shes kyi sku dang /
NK050(wi)011:637: mtshan ma med pa chos kyi sku chos dbyings dmigs
NK050(wi)011:638: pa med pa la rim bzhin dmigs pas snga ma
NK050(wi)011:639: snga ma btang ste spros pa dang bral ba'i ngang
NK050(wi)011:641: de'i ngang las bdag tha mal ba rnam smin gyi
NK050(wi)011:642: lus su gnas pa'i rnam par ldang la sgyu ma
NK050(wi)011:643: la sogs pa'i tshul du lta zhing ngal bso bar
NK050(wi)011:644: bya'o // mdor na ji srid bzlas pa byed pa de srid du /
NK050(wi)011:645: bsam gtan dang ldan par bzla dgos pas /
NK050(wi)011:646: yid rnam par mi rtog pa'i bdag nyid byang chub
NK050(wi)011:647: kyi sems zla ba dri ma med pa'i dkyil 'khor
NK050(wi)011:648: du snang ba la dmigs pa shin tu goms pa'i
NK050(wi)011:649: gsal snang skye zhing mi 'gyur ba de ni gsang
NK050(wi)011:650: sngags kyi phreng ba'i yi gara ldan pa bsgom pa
NK050(wi)011:651: de nyid / dngos grub rtsol ba'i gazha mdun du
NK050(wi)011:652: bsgom pa'i sangs rgyas kyi sku nyid kyi thugs kar
NK050(wi)011:653: bsgom pa lasa dngos grub nod pa'i gazha gyur pa
NK050(wi)011:654: bdag lha'i skur bsgom pa'i thugs kar yang da bzhina
NK050(wi)011:656: rang gi lha'i gsang sngags kyi phreng ba de dag
NK050(wi)011:657: gang du gnas shing 'god pa'i gzhi nyid kyi phyir
NK050(wi)011:658: du ni zla ba'i dkyil 'khor gyi rnam pa ga
NK050(wi)011:659: nga du brtag pa yida kyi rang bzhin rnam par
NK050(wi)011:660: daga pa byang chub sems kyis bdag nyid can de
NK050(wi)011:661: ni nan tan du bsam para bya'o //
NK050(wi)011:662: zhes tshigs bcad 'dis bdag mdun gnyis ka'i thugs kar
NK050(wi)011:663: zla ba dang sngags phreng 'god pa la dmigs par
NK050(wi)011:664: bstan to // de yang ma yengs par nan tan
NK050(wi)011:665: du bya dgos pas mig sogs dbang po'i sgo nas
NK050(wi)011:667: rang gi lus kyi nang du slar sdud pa yasa
NK050(wi)011:668: phyir mi 'phro zhing mi g.yo bar bkug nasa ni
NK050(wi)011:669: / srog rlung dang rtsola ba yid kyi 'gyu dran
NK050(wi)011:670: gnyis ka mi 'pho bar gcig tu bsdama pa'i yid
NK050(wi)011:671: / ni / gasnga sngagas kyi tshul shes shing riga
NK050(wi)011:672: pasa sngagas kyi yi ge la dmigs pa ma yengs
NK050(wi)011:674: de ltar 'byung 'jug gi rlung dang dbang po'i byed
NK050(wi)011:675: pa dang sems kyi dran rtsol sna tshogs rtse gcig
NK050(wi)011:676: mi 'phro bar bsdam pa de la ngag tu brjod
NK050(wi)011:677: pa dbyangs kyis bzlas te mi 'ong pas /
NK050(wi)011:678: yid kyi bzlas brjod 'ba' zhig brtsam par bya'o //
NK050(wi)011:679: srog rtsol bsdam pa sogs 'adi nyid kyis ni cho ga dang ma bral ba yisa /
NK050(wi)011:680: yanga na cung zad lhod pa'i tshul du shub bur bzla ba bya yanga rung mod de /
NK050(wi)011:681: 'on kyang yid bzlas ni mchog yin no //
NK050(wi)011:682: de phyir sngagas rigsa dangsa grub 'doda pa yisa /
NK050(wi)011:683: bshad ma thag pa'i tshul de las ngag tu brjod pa'i bzlas barjada gazhana du mi bya'a //
NK050(wi)011:684: mdor na srog rtsol bsdam zhing dbang po'i sgo nas shes pa yan par mi btang bar /
NK050(wi)011:685: mig zim bu lta stangs cung zad lhod de mdun gyi gzhi sogs gsum la rtse gcig dmigs /
NK050(wi)011:686: bar bar sna'i rlung gtong pa na rang lus lha nyid du blta /
NK050(wi)011:687: ji srid bzlas pa grol gyi bar de ltar bya zhing /
NK050(wi)011:688: rlung phyir 'byin tshe mdun gyi lha yi thugs kar
NK050(wi)011:689: zla ba dang sngags phreng bcas pa mi 'gyur ba
NK050(wi)011:690: la dmigs / nang du rngub tshe bdag gi de
NK050(wi)011:691: gsum la dmigs pa gtso cher bya ba res mos
NK050(wi)011:692: la dmigs / bya zhing / de lta bu'i ngang
NK050(wi)011:693: du gnas pa la yid kyi dag pa zhes bya
NK050(wi)011:694: la dmigs / bya zhing / ste / chags sogs nyon mongs pa ma lang ba'i dag pa dang /
NK050(wi)011:695: dmigs yul gsal la nag nog med pas na dag
NK050(wi)011:696: pa de lta bu la mnyam par bzhag par bya
NK050(wi)011:697: zhing / bzlas pa gtang tshe bdag la ngal gso ba sngar bshad pa bzhin bya'o //
NK050(wi)011:698: mdun gyi lha de rang gi tshad las cung mtho
NK050(wi)011:699: bar bsam zhes slob dpon chen po sangs rgyas gsang
NK050(wi)011:700: bas gsungs so // gnyis pa don bsdu ba /
NK050(wi)011:701: rig sngags de nyid ma lus dang sogs tshigs bcad gcig gis bstan te /
NK050(wi)011:702: rig sngags kyi de kho na nyid lha drug gi tshul du bsgom pa'i rim pa ma lus dang /
NK050(wi)011:703: badga gi de kho na nyida rang bzhin ma grub
NK050(wi)011:704: la snang tsam lha yi sku rang rig 'od gsal
NK050(wi)011:705: gyi ngo bo can du bsgom pa'i cho ga dang
NK050(wi)011:706: / bzlas brjod kyi de kho na nyid yan lag bzhi dang ldan pa /
NK050(wi)011:707: mchoga gi don de nyid rnam pa gsum po 'di legs par shesa na /
NK050(wi)011:708: sngags sgrub par byed pa'i misa ni dngos grub thaba par 'gyur ba la som nyi med do //
NK050(wi)011:709: gnyis pa bzlas brjod kyi yan lag bye brag tu bshad pa la /
NK050(wi)011:710: bzlas brjod kyi de nyid gsum bshad pa dang /
NK050(wi)011:711: rig sngags nye ba sogs kyi tshul bshad pa gnyis /
NK050(wi)011:713: bzlas pa byed pa'i gnas bstan pa dang /
NK050(wi)011:714: bzlas pa'i bsam gtan gyi man ngag de nyid gsum bshad pa gnyis /
NK050(wi)011:716: dben pa'i skyed mos tshal sogs tshigs bcad gcig gis bstan te /
NK050(wi)011:717: bzlas pa byed pa'i gnas ni skye bos dben pa'i
NK050(wi)011:718: skyed mos tshala dang chu bo'i ngogs ri yi phug
NK050(wi)011:719: dang ri bora dang nags tshal sogs mtshan nyid ldan
NK050(wi)011:721: rab tu byung ba dang rig sngags kyi brtul zhugsa la gansa sama /
NK050(wi)011:722: gso sbyong sogs sdoma pa yis rgyud bsdam pa'i sngags
NK050(wi)011:723: sgrub pa po bzlas brjod kyi bsam gtan byed cinga
NK050(wi)011:724: gansa par bya'o // gnyis pa la lam dngos dang /
NK050(wi)011:725: de'i yan lag bshad pa gnyis /
NK050(wi)011:729: gsang sngags mer gnas sogs tshigs bcad gcig gis bstan te /
NK050(wi)011:730: sngags ngag tu brjod pa'i bzlas pa med par bsam gtan gyi sgo nas grub tshul gsungs pa /
NK050(wi)011:731: gasnga sngags mer gansa pa sgom pas 'dod pa'i dngosa grub ster ba dang sgra gnas kyis /
NK050(wi)011:732: ting nge 'dzin gyi rnal 'abyor ster bar dran te
NK050(wi)011:733: 'di gnyis mngon par 'dod pa'i dngos grub 'grub pa'i
NK050(wi)011:735: sgra mathara dmigs na thara pa ster ba nyid de /
NK050(wi)011:736: 'ad daga ni sngags bzla ba'i bsam gtan gyi da nyid gsuma po zhes bya ba yina no //
NK050(wi)011:737: gnyis pa rgyas bshad la nang gi dbye ba so so yod kyang spyir bsdoms te /
NK050(wi)011:738: mi 'byed las byung zhes pa nas /
NK050(wi)011:739: blo gros zhi ba brtan par spyad /
NK050(wi)011:740: ces pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK050(wi)011:741: dbang shes kyis mi 'byed pa yid de /
NK050(wi)011:742: de las byung ba sems dang sems byung gi dngosa po rnams /
NK050(wi)011:743: blo gros cana gyisa ni badga gi de kho na nyid gnyis su med pa la'am /
NK050(wi)011:744: de ltar min na'ang nang du'ang yid nyid la bsdus
NK050(wi)011:745: te bsdamas pas kun nas dkris pa mi 'byung ba'o
NK050(wi)011:746: // de nas sngagsa pa de bdag gnyis kyi spros
NK050(wi)011:747: pa'i yan lag kun las 'das pa snang ba med
NK050(wi)011:748: pa'i ye shes la gansa par byas nas /
NK050(wi)011:749: bsam gtan gyi spyod yul gang la'ang zhena pa med para bsam pa'am bsgom para bya' //
NK050(wi)011:750: 'di ni bsgom pa rnams kyi sngon du 'gro ba dang /
NK050(wi)011:751: gnas skabs kun tu yang 'jug pa yin no //
NK050(wi)011:752: de la sgra gnas zhes pa la sogs pa gsum po de ci lta bu zhe na /
NK050(wi)011:754: sgra zhasa bya ba ni sngags kyi yi ge phreng
NK050(wi)011:755: bar sbyar ba yi sgra gdangs rtog ngor snang ba
NK050(wi)011:756: de yin la / sngags kyi yi ga rnams brgyus la ste gcig gi rjes su gcig 'brel zhing /
NK050(wi)011:757: mi 'gyur ba rnams zhes pa bar ma chad par gsal snang brtan pa'o //
NK050(wi)011:758: de dper na dril bu'i sgra bzhina bar ma chada
NK050(wi)011:759: par brgyud mar sngags kyi yi ge'i sgra gdangs 'byung
NK050(wi)011:761: sngags kyi sgra de lha'i ngo bor shes par bya zhing /
NK050(wi)011:762: sngags kyi sgra gdangs yid ngor snang ba de yida
NK050(wi)011:763: la zhen par gyur pa'i tshul gyis samas pa na
NK050(wi)011:764: / sgra gnas kyi bsam gtan zhes bya'o //
NK050(wi)011:765: mer gnas ni thugs kar ma yi nang nasa sngags kyi sgra de 'byung zhing /
NK050(wi)011:766: me des sngags 'bru la gnod pa sogs med par zha ba sta /
NK050(wi)011:767: sngags 'bru'i tshig rnams chad lhag med par daga pa dang /
NK050(wi)011:768: so so'i rang sgra gsal bar zur phyin pa'i yan lag dang ldana pa de lta bu /
NK050(wi)011:769: srog dang rtsol ba'ang nang du bsdus te bdag gi
NK050(wi)011:770: de kho na nyid du bakaga pa'i badga nyid du
NK050(wi)011:772: gnyid sogs zhum rmug spangsa nasa ni rtse gcig tu rnama par bsam par bya'o //
NK050(wi)011:773: slar yang de'i tshul gsal bar gsungs pa /
NK050(wi)011:774: bdag gi snying gar gansa pa'i phra ba ni /
NK050(wi)011:775: zhes rnam par mi rtog pa'i gzugs brnyan thog reg
NK050(wi)011:776: med cing go ma rdug pa'i phyir rags pa'i dgos
NK050(wi)011:779: dwang zhing 'od gsal ba dri meda zla ba'i dkyila 'akhara te /
NK050(wi)011:780: zla dkyil de yina na mi gnod cing zug rngu
NK050(wi)011:781: med la yid du 'ong ba'i rang bzhin can yin
NK050(wi)011:782: pas na raba tu zha ba ya ma lce raba
NK050(wi)011:784: mi 'gyur pa sngags kyi yi ge'i gzhi yig 'bru rnams ni dera bazhaga nasa /
NK050(wi)011:785: g.yeng ba sogs kyis skyon med par bade bar 'dug nasa /
NK050(wi)011:786: me la gnas pa'i sngags kyi sgra gdangs bsam par bya zhes so //
NK050(wi)011:787: mam zhes pa 'dam nga'i don te /
NK050(wi)011:788: de ltar me yi nang na gnas pa'i sngags kyi
NK050(wi)011:789: sgra gdangs yid kyis bsam nas yid bzlas bya ba'am
NK050(wi)011:790: / yang na lha'i thugs kar ma 'gyur ba byang
NK050(wi)011:791: chub sems kyi ngo bo zla dkyil la sngags kyi
NK050(wi)011:792: ya ge bazhaga pa ni gzugs mi sgom gyi sngags
NK050(wi)011:793: kyi sgra nyid 'ab'a zhiga bsam para bya'o //
NK050(wi)011:794: ngag tu brjod pa med par sngags kyi sgra la
NK050(wi)011:795: dmigas pa'i bsam gtan ni 'ab'a zhiga byas pa nyid
NK050(wi)011:796: kyis kyanga lha dang mi sogs brtan g.yo'i dangos pa
NK050(wi)011:797: kun la gansa pa dama pa'i dapala te dpal bzang
NK050(wi)011:798: po ji snyed yod pa de rnams sgrub pa' skyes
NK050(wi)011:799: bus mtshon pas bud med sogs gang yin des thoba
NK050(wi)011:800: para 'agyur ro // zhes dngos grub ci 'dod pa 'grub ces pa'i tha tshig go //
NK050(wi)011:801: de ltar srog rtsol bsdam ste mer gnas kyi bsam
NK050(wi)011:802: gtan bsgom pas bkres pas mi nyes pa sogs mtshan
NK050(wi)011:803: ma 'byung zhing shin tu sbyang ba thob nas rang
NK050(wi)011:804: gang bsam gyi 'bras bu thob pa'i bar du brtson
NK050(wi)011:805: par bya'o // 'di lta bu'i bzlas brjod kyi bsam
NK050(wi)011:806: gtan ni khyad par 'phags pa'i man ngag yin te
NK050(wi)011:807: par bya'o // / tshul 'di dang ldan na /
NK050(wi)011:808: sems kyi bzhon par gyur pa'i rta dang 'dra ba
NK050(wi)011:809: rlung dang zhon byed sems gnyis ka lhan cig bcings
NK050(wi)011:810: pa'i srog rtsol bsdam pa'i bzlas pa'i ting 'dzin khyad
NK050(wi)011:811: par can myur du 'grub pa de lta bu bzlas
NK050(wi)011:812: pa gzhan gyis mi nus la /
NK050(wi)011:813: yan lag bzhi dang ldan pa'i bzlas brjod 'di lha
NK050(wi)011:814: dang sngags dang de kho na nyid kyi rnam pa
NK050(wi)011:815: lam byed pa'i thabs khyad par can yin pas dngos
NK050(wi)011:816: grub myur du 'thob cing lam gyi rtogs pa myur
NK050(wi)011:818: mer gnas pa dang sgra yi bsam gtan dag kyang
NK050(wi)011:819: sngags kyi stobs bskyed pa yin pas thun rnams su
NK050(wi)011:821: gsum pa sgra mtha'i bsam gtan ni /
NK050(wi)011:822: sgra mtha' zhes pa sgra yal ba ste /
NK050(wi)011:823: yal ba'i gnas ni rang bzhin rnal ma chos sku'i gnas so //
NK050(wi)011:825: de mngon par byed pa dang /
NK050(wi)011:826: rang bzhin yongs su btang ba gsum gyis sngags kyi sgrar snang ba'i rtog pa gtong ste /
NK050(wi)011:827: gnas ni gzugs kyi yan lag gi yig 'brur dmigs pa btang ba'o //
NK050(wi)011:828: mngon byed ni yid bzlas dang shub bzlas kyi sgra'o //
NK050(wi)011:829: rang bzhin ni sgrar snang ba btang ba'o //
NK050(wi)011:830: de lta bu'i don de nyid bstan pa'i phyir gsungs pa /
NK050(wi)011:831: sgra'i gnas su gyur pa'am bzlas brjod 'byung ba'i gzhi
NK050(wi)011:832: ltos pa dang bcas pa'i yan lag tu gyur para
NK050(wi)011:833: snang ba sngags pa'i lus lhar bsgom pa sogs kyi
NK050(wi)011:834: ltos bcas ci rtsol ba thams cad dang /
NK050(wi)011:835: shub bur brjod pa'i sngags kyi sgra zhesa bya ba dang /
NK050(wi)011:836: yid kyi ngora snang ba'i bzlas pa dang /
NK050(wi)011:837: sngags kyi sgrar snang ba'i tshig rnams snang med chos
NK050(wi)011:838: kyi dbyings la dmigs pa btang nas rnam par daga
NK050(wi)011:839: pa ni riga sngagsa dabnga po ste sngags kyi rgyal
NK050(wi)011:840: po yin la / chos thams cad kyi chos nyid dam chos kyi dbyings /
NK050(wi)011:841: spros pa'i mtshan ma'am yan lag thams cad spangsa pa
NK050(wi)011:842: 'di ni sngags sogs chos kun gyi de kho na
NK050(wi)011:843: nyid du / rgyal bas mkhyen cing thugs su chud pa'o //
NK050(wi)011:844: de bsgom pas sgrib pa gnyis las grol bar byed do //
NK050(wi)011:845: ltos bcas zhes pa'i don slar yang bshad pa slar sdud dang /
NK050(wi)011:846: daka'a thub dang yan lag bzhi dang ldan pa'i bsam gtan dang /
NK050(wi)011:848: dkyil 'khor 'bri ba dang mchod pa dang sbyin sreg sogs cho ga'i bya ba thams cad dang /
NK050(wi)011:849: bdag gi de nyid gtan la 'bebs pa'i phyir shes rab kyis dpyad pa byed pa sogs /
NK050(wi)011:850: mdor na rnama para shasa pa sna tshogsa pa'i rtsol
NK050(wi)011:851: ba la gnas pa'i sngagsa pa rnams ni re shaga
NK050(wi)011:852: ste de'i tshe de'i dus na ltos pa dang bcas
NK050(wi)011:853: pa'o // de ltar ltos bcas sam mtshan bcas kyi
NK050(wi)011:854: rnal 'byor la brtson pa'i tshe na sgo gsum rab
NK050(wi)011:855: tu bsdam pa nyon mongs pa'i gnyen po'i dka' thuba
NK050(wi)011:856: chena po rgyun chags shing ma nyams pa dang ldana
NK050(wi)011:857: pa'o // para byas te / bdag gi de kho
NK050(wi)011:858: na nyid phyin ci ma log par rtogs pa'i chos
NK050(wi)011:859: pa'o // para byas te / / rang rgyud la
NK050(wi)011:860: bskyed pa'i thabs rig sngags kyi brtul zhugasa machaga dang
NK050(wi)011:861: pa'o // para byas te / / ldana pa /
NK050(wi)011:862: slar sdud pa sogs sngags kyi yan lag thams cad
NK050(wi)011:863: la ltos pa dang bcas pa ni /
NK050(wi)011:864: gzugs sogs phyi rol yul gyi 'ching ba lasa rnam
NK050(wi)011:865: par grol zhing lha'i byin gyis rlabs nas sngags grub
NK050(wi)011:866: par 'gyur bas / lha sku'i rnam pa'i yan lag
NK050(wi)011:867: gam cha shas sam spros pa dang bcas pa'i rnam
NK050(wi)011:868: par 'gyur bas / par snang ba / mtshan bcas
NK050(wi)011:869: kyi ting nge 'dzin la nan tan du 'bad par
NK050(wi)011:870: par 'gyur bas / par snang ba / bya'o //
NK050(wi)011:871: de ltar na'ang mtshan bcas kyi snang ba 'di dag
NK050(wi)011:872: rnam par rtog pa dang bcas pa yang dag pa'i
NK050(wi)011:874: sngags sgrubs pa lam la brtson pa des mchog 'grub pa'i slad du /
NK050(wi)011:875: ltos bcas kyi gnas skabs der yanga brtul zhugsa te
NK050(wi)011:876: yi dam du goms par re shig byas nasa ni
NK050(wi)011:878: yang dag pa'i don mi gsal ba spang gnyen nam
NK050(wi)011:879: blang ba dang dor ba'i gnyis 'dzin gyi dbang gis
NK050(wi)011:880: / dogas pa'i 'du shes kyi bdag nyid can 'ajaga rten pa'i chos las ma 'das shing /
NK050(wi)011:881: 'jig rten las 'das pa yang dag pa'i chos la
NK050(wi)011:882: ltos na smad pa ya bsam gatana 'ba' zhig gam
NK050(wi)011:883: gciga pu la mngon par zhen cing rloms pa de
NK050(wi)011:884: lta bu yid la mi byed pa'i sgo nas raba
NK050(wi)011:886: chos thams cad rang bzhin gyis ma skyes ma 'gag
NK050(wi)011:887: pa mtha' bzhi'i spros pa dang bral ba'i rnam kun
NK050(wi)011:888: mchog ldan gyi stong nyid chos kyi dbyings la mnyam
NK050(wi)011:889: par bzhag ste mtshan med kyi bsam gtan byed pa
NK050(wi)011:890: ni blo grosa zhi ba zhes bya ste /
NK050(wi)011:891: mtshan 'dzin gyi 'du shes sna tshogs dang sgrib gnyis
NK050(wi)011:892: kyi mun pa zhi ba rnam par rtog pa thams
NK050(wi)011:893: cad dang bral ba'i 'od gsal ba yin pas /
NK050(wi)011:894: de las gzhan du mi 'gyur bar brtan pa nyid spyad par bya'o //
NK050(wi)011:895: zhes 'dis mtshan med kyi rnal 'byor bstan to //
NK050(wi)011:896: de ltar mtshan bcas thabs kyi rnal 'byor gyis 'og
NK050(wi)011:897: min pa'i bar gyi dngos grub ci 'dod pa bde
NK050(wi)011:898: myur du bsgrub pa'i sgo nas 'jigs dang sdug bsngal
NK050(wi)011:899: phral du dbugs dbyung zhing bde ba'i rten las byang
NK050(wi)011:900: chub kyi rigs dang ldan pa'i sgrub pa po skal
NK050(wi)011:901: pa chen por gyur pa des /
NK050(wi)011:902: mtshan med kyi rnal 'byor la goms pas rnam par grol ba mngon du byed cing /
NK050(wi)011:903: yang dag pa'i don du mtshan bcas dang mtshan med
NK050(wi)011:904: kyi rnal 'byor zung du zhugs pa rnam pa kun
NK050(wi)011:905: gyi mchog dang ldan pa'i stong nyid rang bzhin 'od
NK050(wi)011:906: gsal ba'i ye shes chen po lam du byas pa
NK050(wi)011:907: la brten nas mi gnas pa'i 'bras bu sku gnyis
NK050(wi)011:908: zung 'jug gi sangs rgyas nyid mngon du byed par
NK050(wi)011:909: 'gyur ro // gnyis pa lam gyi yan lag ni /
NK050(wi)011:910: khu ba bshang gci sogs nas /
NK050(wi)011:911: rab tu gsang ba gsungs pa yin //
NK050(wi)011:912: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK050(wi)011:913: 'di la nang gses su gtsang sbra bya ba /
NK050(wi)011:914: gzhan la gnod pa spang pa /
NK050(wi)011:915: brtul zhugs ma nyams par bya ba gsum gyi dang po /
NK050(wi)011:916: sngags 'grub pa ni rgyu rkyen rten 'brel la ltos pa'i phyir /
NK050(wi)011:917: sngags bsgrub pa'i yan lag gi spang blang rnams kyang ma 'chol bar spyad dgos te /
NK050(wi)011:920: gaca ba 'dor ba daga dang ni /
NK050(wi)011:921: bza' ba sogs mi gtsang ba dang 'abga pa dag
NK050(wi)011:922: dang na 'og rlung rgyu ba la'ang lhar bsgom ma
NK050(wi)011:923: bsgom gyi skabs kun du'ang sems yan par byas nas
NK050(wi)011:924: bab bab tu mi bya bar bag yod pa'am /
NK050(wi)011:925: dogas pa ya na gzungs te dran shes ma nyams pa rgyun chags pa'i sgo de nyid kyis kyang /
NK050(wi)011:926: dabna para gatsanga sbra la gnas pa brtsam para bya
NK050(wi)011:927: ste gtsang sbra med pa ni bya rgyud kyi tshul
NK050(wi)011:933: gronga dang ganga lhas daga la yanga /
NK050(wi)011:934: ngaga dang lus dang yid kyis spang ba ni /
NK050(wi)011:935: samas cana gnoda pa mi dge bcu po kun mi
NK050(wi)011:936: spyad de spyad na de dag sngags 'grub pa'i 'gal
NK050(wi)011:938: gsum pa sngags 'grub pa'i mthun rkyen /
NK050(wi)011:939: mer gnas sogs bsam gtan dang ni yan lag bzhi ldan gyi bzlas barjada dang /
NK050(wi)011:940: gsang sngags grub para bya ba yi ched du mchod pa dang tshogs bsags pa sogs dang /
NK050(wi)011:941: sbyin sreg bya ba dang dkyil 'khor du dbang bskur ba sogs kyi las thams cada dang /
NK050(wi)011:942: sngags bsgrub pa'i gnas sam yul brtag pa dang /
NK050(wi)011:944: byi dor bya tshe lha'i nga rgyal bya ba sogs
NK050(wi)011:945: mdor na yul gyi ba rnamas la yanga bartul zhugs
NK050(wi)011:946: 'di dang 'di lta bu dgos zhes gsungsa pa ganga
NK050(wi)011:947: yin pa da ya gansa gang du bya ba'am gnas
NK050(wi)011:948: skabs dang / bzlas pa'i grangs la sogs pa'i tshad rnamas kyang /
NK050(wi)011:949: sngon gyi tshe ni badga tshangs pa sa yi me tog nyid /
NK050(wi)011:950: 'ab'a zhiga la mathu stobs chena pa dpal rda rja 'dzin gyi lhas /
NK050(wi)011:951: gzhan la raba tu gasnga ba 'di dag zhal nas
NK050(wi)011:952: dngos su gsungsa shing gadmas pa yina gyi rang bzo
NK050(wi)011:954: skabs 'dir yul gyi bya ba'am gnas kyi bya ba
NK050(wi)011:955: zhes gsungs pa 'di sdod gnas kho nar ma zad
NK050(wi)011:956: 'jug ldog gi / gnas sam yul gong du ma
NK050(wi)011:957: 'dus pa thams cad la go yang chog 'dra snyam
NK050(wi)011:958: 'jug ldog gi / mo // gnyis pa sngags nye ba sogs kyi tshul bshad pa la /
NK050(wi)011:959: mdor bstan te bshad par dam bca' ba dang /
NK050(wi)011:960: de'i rgyas par bshad pa gnyis /
NK050(wi)011:962: nyer gyur mngon du phyogs pa dang /
NK050(wi)011:963: zhes sogs tshigs bcad gcig gis bstan te /
NK050(wi)011:964: de ltar bsam gtan dang bzlas brjod nyid brtson pas
NK050(wi)011:965: bsgrubs pas gsang sngags kyi lha des sgrub pa po
NK050(wi)011:966: byin gyis brlab rung bar mkhyen nas spyan drangs rung
NK050(wi)011:967: ma drangs rung de'i drung du byon pa ni sngags
NK050(wi)011:968: dang / nyer gyur te nye bar gyur pa dang /
NK050(wi)011:969: sngags kyi lha de nyid rang gi gnas der mdun
NK050(wi)011:970: na bzhugs bzhin rang la spyan ras kyis 'tsho ba
NK050(wi)011:971: ni lha mangna du phyogsa pa dang /
NK050(wi)011:972: gasnga sngagas kyi dngos grub mngon du ster bar 'gyur ba dang /
NK050(wi)011:973: mi 'grub par g.yel zhing gazhana du phyogsa pa yi
NK050(wi)011:974: mtshan nyid ganga yana pa da kun tshangsa pa khyod
NK050(wi)011:975: la bashada par bya'o zhes zhal gyis bzhes nas /
NK050(wi)011:977: nye bar gyur pa dang gzhan du phyogs pa'i rgyu bshad pa dang /
NK050(wi)011:978: nye ba sogs kyi mtshan nyid bshad pa gnyis /
NK050(wi)011:981: gzhan du phyogs zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK050(wi)011:982: 'di la nang gses su lha nye ba'i rgyu dang /
NK050(wi)011:983: gzhan du phyogs pa'i rgyu gnyis yod de /
NK050(wi)011:984: de yang lha mngon du nye zhing phyogs pa zhes
NK050(wi)011:985: pa ci lta bu zhe na gasnga sngags dang la
NK050(wi)011:986: sogs pa'i sgras rig sngags dang ldan pa'i riga sngagas
NK050(wi)011:987: kyi khra bo manga pa kun zhes pa'i sgras /
NK050(wi)011:988: rig sngags kyi gtso bo dkyil 'khor gyi lha de
NK050(wi)011:989: nyid la de'i rigs su gtogs pa'i rig sngags kyi
NK050(wi)011:990: khro bo khro mo mngag gzhug pho mo dang bcas
NK050(wi)011:991: pa thams cad gtso bo rgyal ba'i sku la mangna
NK050(wi)011:992: du phyogsa para / bsam gtan gyi bde bas ngomas phyir rtag tu gansa pa yin no //
NK050(wi)011:993: de phyir sgrub pa pos nam rig sngags kyi brtul
NK050(wi)011:994: zhugs mngon du byed pa'i tshe rang gi mdun du
NK050(wi)011:995: de bzhin gshegs pa'i sku bsam la /
NK050(wi)011:996: rig sngags dang gsang sngags dang khro bo khro mo
NK050(wi)011:997: mngag gzhug pho mo sogs nam mkha'i dbyings khyab par
NK050(wi)011:999: rang nyid kyang lha'i gzugs kyis de rnams kyi dbus
NK050(wi)011:1000: sam khrod na 'dug cing sngags kyi brtul zhugs grub
NK050(wi)011:1001: par byin gyis brlab par bsam par bya'o //
NK050(wi)011:1002: de la rig sngags ni rig pa ye shes nyid
NK050(wi)011:1003: sngags kyi gzugs su shar ba'i thabs kyi cha dang
NK050(wi)011:1004: / gsang sngags ni yul chos kyi dbyings nyid mtshan
NK050(wi)011:1005: mar snang ba yum mam shes rab kyi cha yin
NK050(wi)011:1006: / zhing / phan tshun zung du 'brel ba'i phyir rig sngags ni lha mo'i gzugs dbyibs dang /
NK050(wi)011:1007: de ston pa'i sgra dang phyag rgya sogs yin la /
NK050(wi)011:1008: gsang sngags ni de las bzlog ste pho yi dbyibs sogs su'ang gsungs so //
NK050(wi)011:1009: sngags de dag rnam med chos kyi dbyings kyi rang
NK050(wi)011:1010: bzhin du gnas pa don gyi sngags sam don dam
NK050(wi)011:1011: bden pa dang / de'i byin rlabs rtags su shar
NK050(wi)011:1012: ba sngags dang phyag rgya sogs rtags kyi sngags sam
NK050(wi)011:1013: kun rdzob bden pa zhes bya zhing bden gnyis dbyer
NK050(wi)011:1014: med du gnas pa ni mthar thug gi sngags so
NK050(wi)011:1015: bden pa dang / // de ltar shes par byas nas /
NK050(wi)011:1016: rig sngags kyi lha 'khor dang bcas pa de'i mdun du bdag gnas nas /
NK050(wi)011:1017: snga dro dang nyin gung phyi dro yi dus gsum
NK050(wi)011:1018: du ni sngar bshad pa'i yid kyi las phra ma
NK050(wi)011:1019: bsam gtan bya ba 'ad gsang sngags sgrub pa la
NK050(wi)011:1020: brtson pa'am brtun pa de yasa tshangsa pa zhes bos
NK050(wi)011:1021: nas rtag tu raga par bya ba zhes nyams su
NK050(wi)011:1023: sngags nye zhing phyogs pa'i rgyu'i gtso bo 'di yin pa'i phyir na'o //
NK050(wi)011:1024: der ma zad yan lag bcu ya cho ga lasa
NK050(wi)011:1025: ma 'das par rtag tu rig par bya ba'ang yin
NK050(wi)011:1029: bzlas brjod kyi de nyid gsum dang /
NK050(wi)011:1032: sgra mtha'i bsam gtan gsum dang /
NK050(wi)011:1033: sgrub pa la 'jug pa'i cho ga /
NK050(wi)011:1036: gnas kyi bya ba'i nan tan te bcu po de
NK050(wi)011:1037: las skabs su gang bab pa la nan tan du
NK050(wi)011:1038: bya zhing / de dang lhan cig lha'i rnal 'byor
NK050(wi)011:1039: gyi mtshan nyid rig sngags kyi brtul zhugs de mngon
NK050(wi)011:1040: bya zhing / du bya'o // zhes gsungs te /
NK050(wi)011:1041: lha'i rnal 'byor bya ba la gsang sngags las byung
NK050(wi)011:1042: ba'i las kyi bye brag sbyor ba'i mtshan nyid mdor
NK050(wi)011:1043: bsdu na bcu po de tsam du zad pa yin
NK050(wi)011:1044: no // de ltar yan lag bcu dang ldan par
NK050(wi)011:1045: bzlas pa'i bsam gtan la 'bad pa 'di dag sngags
NK050(wi)011:1046: nye zhing mngon du phyogs la dngos grub rtsol ba'i
NK050(wi)011:1047: rgyu yin pas nan tan du bya'o //
NK050(wi)011:1048: sngags g.yel zhing gzhan du phyogs pa'i rgyu ni /
NK050(wi)011:1050: snyom las su gyur pa dang /
NK050(wi)011:1051: bkres skom gyis zala gnona nas bsgrub mi nus pa yang da bzhina te /
NK050(wi)011:1052: gzhan nad la sogs pa yang de bzhin du shes par bya'o //
NK050(wi)011:1053: rnam rtog 'phro zhing rgada pa dang 'gyod pa mya ngan sogs yida kyi gdung ba dang /
NK050(wi)011:1054: sngags sam sngags kyi 'bras bu'am sngags kyi lasa la the tshoma za ba dang /
NK050(wi)011:1055: bzlas brjod dang bsam gtan la yid rtse gcig tu mi zhena pa dang /
NK050(wi)011:1056: sgo gsum dran shes kyis bsdama pa daga na bashaga ste tha mal du gnas pa dang /
NK050(wi)011:1057: cala cola gyi gtam la raba tu dada cing mang du smra ba dang /
NK050(wi)011:1058: mi bya ba ste bya mi rung ba la 'jug pa dang /
NK050(wi)011:1059: phyi'i rkyen gdon rigs loga 'adren gyis ni rgyud barlamasa pa dang /
NK050(wi)011:1060: de'i dbang gis kun rtog ngan pa 'khrug cing /
NK050(wi)011:1061: rma lam ngana pa rnams kyang mathanga ba dang /
NK050(wi)011:1062: semas can daga la gnoda pa'i las byed pa dang /
NK050(wi)011:1063: lha rnamas la ni ma dad cing yongs su smod pa dang /
NK050(wi)011:1064: 'di dang 'di lta bu'i bya ba rnams sgrub pa
NK050(wi)011:1065: pa sngags bzla ba la brtson pa ya cho ga
NK050(wi)011:1066: la 'jug pa ganga gi tshe 'ad dag byed pa
NK050(wi)011:1067: na / rtag tu nada sogs kyis 'atsha ba 'byung bar 'gyur zhing /
NK050(wi)011:1068: gsang sngags ni da lasa gazhana du phyogsa par 'gyur te /
NK050(wi)011:1069: 'di ltar mi 'dod pa'i bag chags bslad nas ya
NK050(wi)011:1070: nga ba ma spang bar las dang nyon mongs kyi
NK050(wi)011:1071: mthus sngags kyi byin rlabs kyi skal ba la gegs
NK050(wi)011:1072: byed pa dag 'byung ba yin pas /
NK050(wi)011:1073: blo dang ldan pa dag gis thabs sna tshogs kyi
NK050(wi)011:1074: sgo nas nyes pa de dag ci nus su gzhil
NK050(wi)011:1076: gsang sngags mi 'grub pa'i gegs ni /
NK050(wi)011:1077: rang gi sngon las mi dge ba dang /
NK050(wi)011:1079: skye bos sdang ba dang nad sogs rnam smin ngan pa gsum du 'du la /
NK050(wi)011:1080: las kyi gegs byed pa zhi phyir bdag med pa'i
NK050(wi)011:1081: bsam gtan bsgom pa dang bzlas pa dang sbyin sreg
NK050(wi)011:1082: sogs gnyen po la 'bad par bya'o //
NK050(wi)011:1083: sngags bzlas kyang ma dad pa sogs rang rgyud kyi
NK050(wi)011:1084: rnam rtog ngan pas gegs byas na rgyu ma tshang
NK050(wi)011:1085: ba'i phyir sngags mi 'grub ste rang skal pa dman
NK050(wi)011:1086: pa'i phyir ro // de lta na'ang rnam rtog ngan
NK050(wi)011:1087: pa rnams so sor rtog pa'i shes rab kyis sun
NK050(wi)011:1088: pa'i phyir ro // 'byin pa dang / mtshang phug
NK050(wi)011:1089: btol te rang bzhin med par 'dul bar bya zhing
NK050(wi)011:1090: pa'i phyir ro // 'byin pa dang / / g.yeng
NK050(wi)011:1091: bas sems las su mi rung ba ni ting nge
NK050(wi)011:1092: 'dzin la brtson pas gdul bar bya'o //
NK050(wi)011:1093: skye bos sdang ba sogs la thabs ji ltar rigs
NK050(wi)011:1094: pas spangs te bsam gtan gyi tsher ma med par
NK050(wi)011:1095: bya zhing / sgyid ma lug par dad pa brtan
NK050(wi)011:1096: pos sngags bsgrub nas dad pas gsol ba 'debs pa
NK050(wi)011:1097: bya zhing / dang / snying rje'i sems kyis smon
NK050(wi)011:1098: lam rgya chen po legs par bgyis na rim gyis
NK050(wi)011:1099: gegs kun zad nas dngos grub thob par 'gyur ro
NK050(wi)011:1100: bya zhing / dang / // gnyis pa lha nye ba sogs kyi mtshan nyid bshad pa ni /
NK050(wi)011:1101: gang zhig zhi bar 'dug pa dang /
NK050(wi)011:1103: dbang du gyur pa rtag par ro //
NK050(wi)011:1104: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te 'di la 'ang nang gi dbye ba yod mod /
NK050(wi)011:1105: de dag tshig gi don bshad pas rtogs par 'gyur ro //
NK050(wi)011:1106: de yang bzlas brjod dang bsam gtan byed pa ganga zhiga sems las su rung zhing /
NK050(wi)011:1107: dug gsum dang rgyags pa sogs ma langs par sgo gsum rab tu zhi bar 'adug pa dang /
NK050(wi)011:1108: bzlas pa'i bsam gtan la brtson pas rnam par shes
NK050(wi)011:1109: pa sngags kyi sgra ya nga bo gyur pa zhes
NK050(wi)011:1110: / sgra la sems kyis dmigs pa tsam rgyang chad
NK050(wi)011:1111: du snang ba lta bu min par dmigs dang sems
NK050(wi)011:1112: 'dres nas sems nyid sngags kyi rnam par snang ba'i
NK050(wi)011:1113: gsal snang bar ma chad pa las mi g.yo bar
NK050(wi)011:1114: / gyur pa na / da yi tshe sgrub pa
NK050(wi)011:1115: po sngagas pa de ni bsgrub par bya ba'i gsang
NK050(wi)011:1116: sngags la nye bar gyur te lha mngona du phyogsa
NK050(wi)011:1117: / gyur pa na / pa'ang thob bo // ye
NK050(wi)011:1118: shes kyi lha la nye bar gyur pa'am bsnyen pa
NK050(wi)011:1119: / gyur pa na / pa'ang thob bo // dang
NK050(wi)011:1120: / ring bar gyur ba'am bsring ba mi mnga' mod
NK050(wi)011:1121: kyi rang gi las kyi skal ba dang /
NK050(wi)011:1122: sems kyi dbang gis nye ring du snang bar 'gyur ro //
NK050(wi)011:1123: gzhan yang dbang po sogs lha dang /
NK050(wi)011:1124: srin po sogs lha mana gyi semas cana ni /
NK050(wi)011:1125: dabang phyug dang ldan cing mkhyen pa'i ye shesa 'ajug
NK050(wi)011:1126: pa mnga' ba rnamas gang gis mathanga na mi 'dod
NK050(wi)011:1127: pa zhi ba dang phan pa skye bar 'gyur ba
NK050(wi)011:1128: da ni sgrub pa pos mangna du gyur pa ste
NK050(wi)011:1129: dngos su mthong ba dang zhes so //
NK050(wi)011:1130: 'di la lha sogs de lta bu mthong na sngags mngon du gyur pa zhes sbyar kyang rung mod /
NK050(wi)011:1131: rtsa ba'i tshig nus ltar na 'di ltar bshad pa bde bar 'dra'o //
NK050(wi)011:1132: gzhan mi'i rgyal po dang ni 'byor ldan phyug po rnams dang /
NK050(wi)011:1133: skye bo dang bud mada dge ba ste skal pa
NK050(wi)011:1134: bzang po rnamas rang gi dabnga du gyur cing rang
NK050(wi)011:1135: la yid mangna du phyogs pas pus ma 'dzugs shing
NK050(wi)011:1136: spyi bosa 'adud pa'ang phyi'i mtshan ma ste sngags mngon
NK050(wi)011:1138: sngags pa da la blo gros sam shasa pa'ang sngar
NK050(wi)011:1139: med pa skye bar 'gyur zhing sngar ma thosa pa'i
NK050(wi)011:1140: don lta bu yanga bde blag tu shes para 'gyur
NK050(wi)011:1141: ba yid kyi yon tan dang /
NK050(wi)011:1142: skad cig daga la rang gi lus las ni /
NK050(wi)011:1143: bar bar ma bzhina 'od 'byung ba'am 'abra bar 'gyur ba ni nang gi mtshan ma'o //
NK050(wi)011:1144: bar snang sogs las yid du 'ong ba'i glu dang sila snyan gyi sgra rnams dang /
NK050(wi)011:1145: lha rnamas kyis ni gtam smra bar yanga /
NK050(wi)011:1146: lha mngona du phyogsa pa'i sngagas pa yisa de daga rtag tu thasa para 'agyur ba phyi'i mtshan ma'o //
NK050(wi)011:1147: de ltar gsang sngags kyi lha ni mngona du phyogs pa'i sgrub pa po na mathu chen pa /
NK050(wi)011:1148: blo gros can brtson pa drag po'i sgo nas daka'a thuba 'grub pa de yisa /
NK050(wi)011:1149: gsang sngags mngon du phyogs pa las ma nyams shing dngos grub thob pa'i ched du /
NK050(wi)011:1150: bzlas pa dang bsam gtan la kun du zhen pa'i dus rtag tu bya ste /
NK050(wi)011:1151: sngags mngona du phyogsa pa'i gansa thaba na /
NK050(wi)011:1152: gnas skabs su nama makhara rgyu ba ste lha nyid du mangna pa'i gnas thob ste /
NK050(wi)011:1153: ji ltar na rang gi lus lha gzhon nur 'gyur zhing /
NK050(wi)011:1154: sgo gsum po phun sum tshogs pa'i yon tan can /
NK050(wi)011:1155: bde zhing skyid pa'i dabnga phyug gi yon tan manga pa thob ste /
NK050(wi)011:1156: de las mi nyams par rtag tu longs spyod pa nyid du gyur kyang /
NK050(wi)011:1157: ganga zhaga gti mug gi dbang gis 'dod pa'i 'ching
NK050(wi)011:1158: bas ma myos pa de ni sngagas riga pa zhes
NK050(wi)011:1159: bya zhing / de la gasnga sngagas bsgrub pa'i 'abras bu ma lus pa /
NK050(wi)011:1160: ya shes dang dabnga phyug phun sum tshogs pas brgyan pa yanga thaba la /
NK050(wi)011:1161: sgrub pa po de nyid 'dod pa'i yon tan dang
NK050(wi)011:1162: ldan pa'i dga' bas myos pa dang ldan pa'i lha
NK050(wi)011:1163: yi ganas ni mi yi gnas las mchoga tu gyur
NK050(wi)011:1165: de ltar na'ang sngags rig pa de /
NK050(wi)011:1166: ranga gi mathu ye shasa pas rgyud gasla bar gyur
NK050(wi)011:1167: pa'i phyir bag med par 'dod pas myos nas sngags
NK050(wi)011:1168: kyi brtson pa gtong bar mi 'gyur ro //
NK050(wi)011:1169: de ltar gnas skabs su lus sems bde zhing skyid pa'i dbang phyug la longs spyod bzhin /
NK050(wi)011:1170: sngags kyi lam la brtson pa ma btang bar byas pa'i mthar thug gi 'bras bu ni /
NK050(wi)011:1171: sangs rgyas rdo rje lta ba'i sku cana gyi gasnga
NK050(wi)011:1172: ba'i machaga sku gsung thugs kyi 'byor pa mi zad
NK050(wi)011:1173: pa / dag cing tshangsa pa mchog gi go 'phang
NK050(wi)011:1174: 'khor ba'i nyes pa'i skyon meda pa ganga yin pa
NK050(wi)011:1175: pa / / rdzu 'phrul la sogs pa'i yon tan tshad med pa gang zhig thaba nas /
NK050(wi)011:1176: gtan badra 'gyur ba yon tan thams cad yongas su rdzogsa pa rgyal ba bzhina du'o //
NK050(wi)011:1177: de'i phyir sngags sgrub pa ni phan yon dang dgos pa shin tu che ba'i phyir na /
NK050(wi)011:1178: sngags bsgrub pa la gcig tu spro zhing lus sems stobsa dang ldana para ni /
NK050(wi)011:1179: bzlas brjod dang bsam gatana dka' thub kyi gnas la
NK050(wi)011:1180: brtson pa brten pa'i mis gasnga sngags kyi ranga bzhin
NK050(wi)011:1182: sngon gyi tshe rabs brgyud ma nas byas pa'i sdiga pa thams cad bsreg para bya'o //
NK050(wi)011:1183: de yang sngon gyi tshe rabs rnams su byas pa'i
NK050(wi)011:1184: mi dge ba dang nyon mongs pa'i dbang gis phal
NK050(wi)011:1185: cher sngags bsgrub na yang sems las ru mi rung
NK050(wi)011:1186: ba dang / nad dang gdon sogs rkyen sna tshogs pas gegs byed pa 'byung na yang /
NK050(wi)011:1187: sngags la brtson pa ma btang na sdig pa rnams kyang rim pas byang bar 'gyur la /
NK050(wi)011:1188: bsam gtan la brtson pa lus sems shin tu sbyang ba 'thob par 'gyur te /
NK050(wi)011:1189: 'di ltar gansa dang kha zasa dang granga ba chara
NK050(wi)011:1190: dang rlung dang tsha ba rnams la lus kyis bzod
NK050(wi)011:1191: cing sems kyis ci mi snyam para nam zhig 'gyur
NK050(wi)011:1192: na de yi tshe sngags bsgrub pa'i lasa kyi 'brasa
NK050(wi)011:1193: bu chud mi za bar nyams su myong bar ngesa
NK050(wi)011:1194: par 'gyur ro // 'di ni gtso bor lus kyi ngang brtan par gyur pa'i yon tan no //
NK050(wi)011:1195: yid kyi yon tan sngags zla ba'i tshe bzla bya'i
NK050(wi)011:1196: sngags kyi sgra'am yanga na lha'i gzugas la'ang ganga brtsona
NK050(wi)011:1197: pa'am dmigs pa'i tshe na ni mi rmongsa pa ste
NK050(wi)011:1198: rang byan tshud pa'i sher ting gsal ba na sngags
NK050(wi)011:1199: nye bar gyur pa de shesa para bya'o //
NK050(wi)011:1200: sngags la brtson pa'i daka'a thuba cana gyis phyi dang
NK050(wi)011:1201: nang gi nye bar 'tshe ba'i gnoda pa spangsa te
NK050(wi)011:1202: de dag gis mi gnod la /
NK050(wi)011:1203: sgrub pa po ganga zhig mthonga ba tsam gyis ni /
NK050(wi)011:1204: mi dang mi min sbrul dang gcan gzan sogs semas
NK050(wi)011:1205: cana thams cad byamsa par 'gyur ba da na dangsa
NK050(wi)011:1206: grub nye bar 'gyur ba yin no //
NK050(wi)011:1207: gzhan thams cad byams pas na de la 'gal bar
NK050(wi)011:1208: byed pa'i baggas rnams thams cad kyanga rnam para spangsa
NK050(wi)011:1210: de lta na bsrung ba sogs mi dgos sam zhe na /
NK050(wi)011:1211: bad ba dang ni sdug bsngal gyi las snang gi mtha' la spyod pa dang /
NK050(wi)011:1212: bde ba la 'doda pa dang sdug bsngal la khro ba dang /
NK050(wi)011:1213: dgra sogs kyis 'jigas pa dang nada dang 'chi ba
NK050(wi)011:1214: dang gnoda pa sna tshogs pa daga gi rgyu na
NK050(wi)011:1215: nang rang gi rgyud kyi bag chags yin la de
NK050(wi)011:1216: ni sngagsa pa gang zhig gnas skabs su gnod pa
NK050(wi)011:1217: sna tshogs dang bral ba rnams la'ang yoda pas /
NK050(wi)011:1218: gnod pa srung zhing bsal ba'i las la brtson pa ni dgos pa yod do //
NK050(wi)011:1219: nang gi rgyu de rkyen dang phrad na bar du
NK050(wi)011:1220: gcod pa'i bgegs dang gegs su gyur pa 'byung srid
NK050(wi)011:1221: pa'i phyir ro // nama zhig sngags shin tu nye bar gyur pa de'i tshe na /
NK050(wi)011:1222: da lta'i dus tshod dang yul dang bya ba'i khyad par dang /
NK050(wi)011:1223: sngon gyi lasa chosa mina gyi 'brasa bu smin pa la /
NK050(wi)011:1224: de tshe sngagsa pa cung zad kyang mi ltos so //
NK050(wi)011:1225: riga sngagsa nyer gyur 'adda pa ste nye bar gyur
NK050(wi)011:1226: nas rig sngags grub 'dod pa ste grub tu cha
NK050(wi)011:1227: ba dang ral gri sogs kyi dngos grub pa dang
NK050(wi)011:1228: ni de bazhana du mchog thob pa de yi tshe
NK050(wi)011:1229: na sngar nyes pa stong daga byas pa yin na
NK050(wi)011:1230: yanga / bzoda par 'gyur bar dogas pa meda de /
NK050(wi)011:1231: skabs 'dir dngos grub thob pa la sngar gyi nyes pas cung zad g.yo bar mi nus so //
NK050(wi)011:1232: de ltar na sngon gyi las dang da lta'i dus
NK050(wi)011:1233: sogs rkyen rnams kyis dngos grub thob pa'i tshogs pa
NK050(wi)011:1234: tshang pa la gegs byed pa yin na'ang rig sngags
NK050(wi)011:1235: nye zhing dngos grub kyi tshogs pa tshang nas nus
NK050(wi)011:1236: pa mthu can thogs mar gyur pa'i tshe sngags kyi
NK050(wi)011:1237: nus pa mthu che bas sus kyang bardzi mi nus
NK050(wi)011:1238: te / nor bu 'bad pas btsal ba rnyed par
NK050(wi)011:1239: gyur na 'dod pa ci dgar byin pa lta bu
NK050(wi)011:1240: yin pas gzhan la ltos pa med pa'i phyir sngags
NK050(wi)011:1241: nye ba'i mtshan ma brtan po thob pa na sgrub
NK050(wi)011:1242: pa brtsam par bya ste dus la ltos pa med
NK050(wi)011:1243: te / do // dngos grub thob pa de yang /
NK050(wi)011:1244: ragas las byung ba'i dngos grub dang rdzas las byung ba'i dangsa grub gnyis su dbye ba yod do //
NK050(wi)011:1245: rigs las byung ba zhes pa dngos grub kyi rdzas la ma brten par yang /
NK050(wi)011:1246: mngon shes sam lha sogs dang skal ba mnyam pa'i
NK050(wi)011:1247: dngos grub thob pa la sogs pa ni lha nyid
NK050(wi)011:1248: las thob pas rigs byung zhes bya la /
NK050(wi)011:1249: ral gri dang mig sman sogs grub pa ni rdzas las byung ba yin pa dang /
NK050(wi)011:1250: gzhan yang bcud kyis len pa'i sman gyis yanga ni lus can la /
NK050(wi)011:1251: gsang sngags nye bar gyur pa dang sngagsa mngon du grub pa ni /
NK050(wi)011:1252: grub pa rab 'bring tha ma gang grub kyang /
NK050(wi)011:1253: de dang ltar sngags pas spyad du byung ba'i tshul
NK050(wi)011:1254: gyis rang dabnga du gyur par byed cing rtag par
NK050(wi)011:1256: bzhi pa mjug gi don ni bsam gtan phyi ma rim par phye ba rdzogs so //
NK050(wi)011:1257: shwa lo ka lnga bcu rtsa gsum mo zhes /
NK050(wi)011:1258: bod skad du bstan pa snga dar gyi dus su bsgyur ba'o //
NK050(wi)011:1259: bsam gtan phyi ma'i rgyud kyi don rgya cher bshad
NK050(wi)011:1260: pa mkhas shing dngos grub brnyes pa'i slob dpon sngags
NK050(wi)011:1261: phyi rgyud kyi shing rta chen po sangs rgyas gsang
NK050(wi)011:1262: bas mdzad pa lo ts+aa ba chen po ska ba
NK050(wi)011:1263: dpal brtsegs kyis 'gyur ba nyid la brten nas 'grel
NK050(wi)011:1264: pa rigs sngags 'dzin pa'i yid kyi 'dod 'jo zhes
NK050(wi)011:1265: bya ba 'di nyid mi pham 'jam dpal dgyes pa'i
NK050(wi)011:1266: rdo rje zhes bya bas rab tshes me lug chu
NK050(wi)011:1267: stod zla ba'i tshes nyi shu la mgo brtsam nas
NK050(wi)011:1268: phyi nyin nyer gcig pa'i snga dror grub par byas
NK050(wi)011:1269: pa 'dis sngags sgrub pa rnams kyi re ba yid
NK050(wi)011:1270: bzhin du skong ba dang sems can thams cad la
NK050(wi)011:1271: dngos grub rnam gnyis kyi dpal sbyin par gyur cig
NK050(wi)011:1272: / rig sngags bzlas brjod byed par 'dod pa la //
NK050(wi)011:1273: thabs 'di re ba yid bzhin skong ba yi //
NK050(wi)011:1274: rin chen dbang gi rgyal po las lhag pas //
NK050(wi)011:1275: sngags 'dzin rnams kyi snying dbus dga' ston mdzod //
NK050(wi)011:1280: // me glang lor skyabs rje mkhyen sbrul rin po ches
NK050(wi)011:1281: 'di dag spar du bkod dgos pa'i bka'i cod pan
NK050(wi)011:1284: bsam mchan bcas 'phrul spar sgros gtsang legs par bgyis
NK050(wi)011:1285: pa'i bsod nams dpag yas ga nga des bstan pa
NK050(wi)011:1286: mchod yon zung gi zhabs pad brtan cing /
NK050(wi)011:1287: mdzad 'phrin snang ba dkar pos yongs su skyong bas 'gro rnams bde dag'i dpal gyis 'tsho ba dang /
NK050(wi)011:1288: bdag kyang skye ba'i phreng bar rgyal ba'i chos mdzod
NK050(wi)011:1289: 'dzin skyong spel la nam yang mi ngal ba 'di
NK050(wi)011:1290: ltar / mi pham 'jam pa'i dbyangs kyi thugs bskyed dang //
NK050(wi)011:1291: mdzad pa smon lam mkhyen brtse nus pa'i tshul //
NK050(wi)011:1292: bla med ye shes sgyu 'phrul ji 'dra ba //
NK050(wi)011:1293: de 'dra kho nar bdag sogs 'gyur bar shog /
NK050(wi)011:1294: ces spar dpon bla ming ting 'dzin chos grags kyis
NK050(wi)011:1295: dge rtsa dang 'brel ba'i smon lam btab pa de
NK050(wi)011:1296: de bzhin du 'grub par gyur cig gu /
